(1, 1, 1, 'Gioi thieu ve Cong ty Chi Thanh', 'Company Profile', '&nbsp;GIOI THIEU C&Ocirc;NG TY \r\n\r\nTh&agrave;nh lap tu nam 2003, den nay sau hon 6 nam hoat dong, C&ocirc;ng Ty Nhua CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N d&atilde; c&oacute; nhung thay doi buoc ngoac, d&aacute;nh dau mot buoc ph&aacute;t trien moi cua c&ocirc;ng ty. \r\nVoi su no luc kh&ocirc;ng ngung, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i d&atilde; x&acirc;y dung th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y chuyen san xuat kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n tu thiet ke v&agrave; che tao khu&ocirc;n mau den lap r&aacute;p th&agrave;nh pham nhung thiet bi chuy&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng, nhung san pham nhua cao cap phuc vu cho nhu cau ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng trong ngo&agrave;i nuoc. Voi ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; CHAT LUONG dat l&ecirc;n h&agrave;ng dau, tat ca san pham cua CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N deu duoc san xuat&nbsp; mot c&aacute;ch nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c theo qui dinh kiem tra, kiem dinh, chung nhan cua c&aacute;c co quan chuc nang. \r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;', '<p align=''center''><br />\r\n<font color=''#cc0000'' size=''4''><strong>INTRODUCTION</strong></font></p>\r\n<p>Established in October 2003, <strong><font color=''#cc0000''>CHI THANH V.N</font></strong> Company is a chain of workshops specializing in different plastic products such as: electric pictures, picture frames, helmet for motorcycle riders, water pumps&hellip;. which have been known nationwide</p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''>&nbsp;<img src=''/envita/upload/image/ISO.jpg'' style=''width: 433px; height: 408px;'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=''margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; text-indent: 0.25in; text-align: justify;'' class=''MsoNormal''>&nbsp;</p>', '&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;GIOI THIEU C&Ocirc;NG TY \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Th&agrave;nh lap tu nam 2003, den nay sau hon 6 nam hoat dong, C&ocirc;ng Ty Nhua CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N d&atilde; c&oacute; nhung thay doi buoc ngoac, d&aacute;nh dau mot buoc ph&aacute;t trien moi cua c&ocirc;ng ty. \r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Voi su no luc kh&ocirc;ng ngung, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i d&atilde; x&acirc;y dung th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y chuyen san xuat kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n tu thiet ke v&agrave; che tao khu&ocirc;n mau den lap r&aacute;p th&agrave;nh pham nhung thiet bi chuy&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng, nhung san pham nhua cao cap phuc vu cho nhu cau ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng trong ngo&agrave;i nuoc. Voi ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; CHAT LUONG dat l&ecirc;n h&agrave;ng dau, tat ca san pham cua CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N deu duoc san xuat&nbsp;mot c&aacute;ch nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c theo qui dinh kiem tra, kiem dinh, chung nhan cua c&aacute;c co quan chuc nang. \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trong nam 2008, CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ty san xuat dau ti&ecirc;n duoc Trung T&acirc;m Ky Thuat Ti&ecirc;u Chuan Do Luong Chat Luong 3- Quatest 3 d&aacute;nh gi&aacute; v&agrave; chung nhan san xuat Mu Bao Hiem ph&ugrave; hop qui chuan quoc gia QCVN 02: 2008/BKHCN. B&ecirc;n canh d&oacute; san pham cua c&ocirc;ng ty c&ograve;n dat duoc nhieu giai thuong kh&aacute;c ve uy t&iacute;n thuong hieu v&agrave; chat luong san pham , duoc nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng ca nuoc b&igrave;nh chon danh hieu H&Agrave;NG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO.\r\nNhung san pham chu yeu hien nay:\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Mu bao hiem cho nguoi di moto, xe m&aacute;y voi 34 kieu d&aacute;ng c&aacute;c loai voi 3 nh&atilde;n hieu: CHITA, OMONO, SAFE ph&ugrave; hop QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Dung cu phuc vu nu&ocirc;i t&ocirc;m c&ocirc;ng nghiep voi day du chung loai, ph&ugrave; hop voi c&aacute;c vi tr&iacute; dia l&yacute; kh&aacute;c nhau.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;D&acirc;y dai, t&uacute;i luoi v&agrave; bao b&igrave; c&aacute;c loai.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Ro dung tr&aacute;i c&acirc;y xuat khau.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nang luc trang thiet bi ch&iacute;nh:\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Hon 50 m&aacute;y &eacute;p nhua c&aacute;c loai tu 50 tan den 550 tan.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Ph&acirc;n xuong che tao khu&ocirc;n mau voi he thong thiet ke CAD/CAM v&agrave; c&aacute;c trang thiet bi dieu khien ky thuat so (CNC) san s&agrave;ng phuc vu c&aacute;c thiet ke kh&aacute;c nhau cua kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Ph&acirc;n xuong san xuat mop xop (EPS) voi c&aacute;c trang thiet bi tu dong phuc vu cho viec san xuat mop l&oacute;t mu bao hiem v&agrave; c&aacute;c loai san pham kh&aacute;c nhau phuc vu c&ocirc;ng, n&ocirc;ng nghiep.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;Ph&acirc;n xuong d&acirc;y dai bao b&igrave; c&aacute;c loai c&oacute; nang luc san xuat hon 4 tan/ng&agrave;y. Hien dang chuan bi dua d&acirc;y chuyen san xuat d&acirc;y cao cap nang suat 1 tan/ng&agrave;y v&agrave;o hoat dong de san xuat nhung loai d&acirc;y dai phuc vu cho c&aacute;c xuong bao b&igrave; d&ograve;i hoi ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tu dong.\r\n&sect;&nbsp;D&acirc;y chuyen san xuat mu bao hiem (MBH) c&oacute; kha nang san xuat tr&ecirc;n 5000 MBH c&aacute;c loai/ng&agrave;y v&agrave; c&oacute; thiet bi kiem dinh &ldquo;d&acirc;m xuy&ecirc;n&rdquo;, va dap v&agrave; hap thu xung dong tai noi san xuat.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nhung giai thuong v&agrave; chung nhan d&atilde; dat duoc:\r\n\r\n    H&Agrave;NG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO-Do nguoi ti&ecirc;u dung b&igrave;nh chon&nbsp; \r\n    Huy Chuong V&agrave;ng v&agrave; chung nhan H&Agrave;NG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO PH&Ugrave; HOP TI&Ecirc;U CHUAN \r\n    C&uacute;p V&agrave;ng THUONG HIEU VIET tr&ecirc;n duong hoi nhap WTO \r\n    Chung nhan 100 THUONG HIEU, SAN PHAM TI&Ecirc;U BIEU UNG DUNG KHOA HOC &amp; C&Ocirc;NG NGHE \r\n    Chung nhan THUONG HIEU SAN PHAM UY T&Iacute;N CHAT LUONG. \r\n    C&uacute;p THUONG HIEU UY T&Iacute;N TAI VN 2007.&nbsp; \r\n\r\nTru so ch&iacute;nh : Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y &eacute;p nhua c&aacute;c loai voi hon 80% m&aacute;y &eacute;p nhua su dung trong d&acirc;y chuyen san xuat mang nh&atilde;n hieu JSW nhap khau tu Nhat Ban.\r\nDia chi: 611 Tran Dai Nghia, phuong T&acirc;n Tao A, quan B&igrave;nh T&acirc;n, Tp.HCM\r\nVan ph&ograve;ng giao dich:\r\nDia chi:122 Duong V&agrave;nh Dai Trong, phuong B&igrave;nh Tri D&ocirc;ng B, quan B&igrave;nh T&acirc;n, Tp.HCM\r\nDien thoai : 08.38170411- Fax: 08.3817 04 08\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '<p align=''center''><font color=''#cc0000''><font size=''3''><strong>INTRODUCTION</strong></font> </font></p>\r\n<p align=''left''><span style=''font-size: small;''>Established in October 2003, <font color=''#cc0000''><strong>CHI THANH V.N PLASTIC COMPANY</strong> </font>is a chain of workshops specializing in different plastic areas such as: electric pictures, picture frames, helmet for motorcycle riders, water pumps&hellip;. which have been known nationwide. During its operation, CHI THANH V.N has ensured the high quality of its product,as well as constantly developed its business to be more competitively productive to serve national industry, agriculture, consumption and export.</span></p>\r\n<p style=''margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;'' class=''MsoNormal''><span style=''font-size: small;''><font face=''VNI-Times''><strong>Head office</strong>: Specialized in pressing plastic. Over 80% of using pressing machine&rsquo;s mark is JSW imported from </font></span><font face=''VNI-Times''><st1:country-region w:st=''on''><st1:place w:st=''on''><span style=''font-size: small;''>Japan</span></st1:place></st1:country-region></font><span style=''font-size: small;''><font face=''VNI-Times''>.</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=''margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;'' class=''MsoNormal''><span style=''font-size: small;''><font face=''VNI-Times''><i style=''''><u>Address</u></i>: 611 Tran </font></span><font face=''VNI-Times''><st1:street w:st=''on''><st1:address w:st=''on''><span style=''font-size: small;''>Dai Nghia Street</span></st1:address></st1:street></font><span style=''font-size: small;''><font face=''VNI-Times''>, Tan Tao A Ward, Binh Tan District, HCMC.</font></span></p>\r\n<p align=''left''><span style=''font-size: small;''><br />\r\n<font face=''VNI-Times''><strong><u>Office:</u></strong><br />\r\n</font><em>Add:</em>122 Vanh Dai Trong&nbsp;,&nbsp;Ward Binh Tri Dong B,&nbsp;District Binh Tan, Ho Chi Minh City<br />\r\n<em>Tel:</em>&nbsp;&nbsp; 848.38170411&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=''font-size: small;''>Fax: 848.3817 04 08</span></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img height=''518'' width=''636'' src=''/envita/upload/image/ISO.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;'' class=''MsoNormal''><font face=''VNI-Times''><span style=''color: black;''><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p><span style=''font-size: small;''>Starting its business as a small enterprise with only 4 small-size plastic pressing machines and handicraft assembly and production line with more than 40 workers, now <font color=''#cc0000''><strong>CHI THANH V.N PLASTIC COMPANY</strong></font> has 5 workshops operating under closed processes with over 200 technicians and staffs and with today&rsquo;s development, the company has offered customers high quality products, and the most competitive price, which helps to meet all market&rsquo;s demands. Not only producing its traditional products, <font color=''#cc0000''><strong>CHI THANH V.N PLASTIC COMPANY</strong></font> is also willing to produce others products at customers&rsquo; requests.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=''font-size: small;''>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=''left''><span style=''font-size: small;''>The company always puts quality of products and competitive price on top priority. For that reason, coming with us, you can feel secure about art, technique of products as well as confidentiality of information about products.</span></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6746_1253771668_resize_1253933356.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6707%20copy_resize_1253933406.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6736%20copy_resize_1253933205.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6757_resize_1253933453.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6782_resize_1253933492.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6896_resize_1253933534.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6785_resize(1)_1253933571.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6891%20copy_resize_1253933629.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6752%20copy_resize_1253934027.jpg'' alt='''' /></p>\r\n<p style=''text-align: center;''><img hspace=''0'' border=''0'' align=''baseline'' src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/img_6898_resize_1253934249.jpg'' style=''width: 555px; height: 400px;'' alt='''' /></p>', '', 1, 1277891015, 'e5e9ee7b605b639eb1e0947f29bebc4c'),
(2, 100, 2, 'Chuong trinh ''VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON''', '', '&nbsp;''VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON ''\r\n\r\nCONG TY CO PHAN BAO HIEM AAA&nbsp;vua trien khai Chuong trinh Dac biet â€œ BAO HIEM AAA- VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON â€ tu ngay 15/11/2006 â€“ 15/12/2006.Trong chuong trinh nay, Bao hiem AAA se tang mu bao hiem cho khach hang di xe gan may khi tham gia bao hiem ........', '', '&nbsp;''VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON ''\r\n\r\nCONG TY CO PHAN BAO HIEM AAA&nbsp;vua trien khai Chuong trinh Dac biet â€œ BAO HIEM AAA- VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON â€ tu ngay 15/11/2006 â€“ 15/12/2006.Trong chuong trinh nay, Bao hiem AAA se tang mu bao hiem cho khach hang di xe gan may khi tham gia bao hiem .Day la chuong trinh mang tinh xa hoi cua Cong ty va gop phan vao chuong trinh An toan giao thong quoc gia . Co the noi, Bao hiem AAA da the hien trach nhiem va tinh nhan van cao doi voi cong dong xa hoi.De dam bao chat luong&nbsp; va su an toan, bao hiem AAA da quyet dinh chon Cong Ty TNHH SX-TM Nhua Chi Thanh VN lam nha cung cap mu bao hiem cho chuong trinh . San pham mu bao hiem cua Chi Thanh VN se co mat trong he thong Bao hiem AAA tren toan quoc.Theo Ong Bui Van Minh â€“ Giam Doc HCTH Cong ty Co phan Bao hiem AAA â€œViec chon Cong Ty TNHH SX-TM Nhua Chi Thanh VN lam nha cung cap mu bao hiem cho chuong trinh la su lua chon dung dan, vi Nhua Chi Thanh VN la doi tac tin cay, uy tin va san pham mu bao hiem Nhua Chi Thanh VN dep ve mau ma, chat luong dat chuan TCVN 5756: 2001 â€\r\nCung vi muc dich tot dep doi voi xa hoi, Cong Ty TNHH SX-TM Nhua Chi Thanh VN quyet dinh danh cho Bao hiem AAA moi dieu kien thuan loi va uu dai de Chuong trinh Dac biet â€œ BAO HIEM AAA- VI CUOC SONG AN TOAN HON â€ se phuc vu dong dao cong chung .', '', '', 0, 1185593644, '65bea2001bcdc729a0dafc29e75ea39a'),
