(27, 92, 2, 'Chuc mung CTY CHI THANH V.N duoc chung nhan hop quy MU BAO HIEM : CHITA-OMONO-SAFE', 'Congratulations to CHI THANH V.N PLASTIC Company whose brands CHITA-OMONO-SAFE  have just achieved confirmation of qualified standard', 'CONG TY CHI THANH V.N CHINH THUC DUOC CHUNG NHAN va CONG BO HOP QUY MU BAO HIEM CHITA-OMONO-SAFE\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ngay sau khi Quyet dinh so 04/2008 cua Bo Khoa hoc-Cong nghe&nbsp; trien khai thuc hien quy chuan Viet Nam 2008 ve chung nhan cong bo hop quy, gan tem chuan CR thay the cho tem CS duoc ban hanh, Ban giam doc CTY CHI THANH V.N da khan truong chi dao Bo phan ky thuat nghien cuu tim hiem quy chuan moi, len ke hoach dieu chinh khuon mau va quy trinh cong nghe san xuat de di dau trong cong cuoc cai tien, nang cap chat luong san pham theo chi dao cua Bo .', '<P align=center>&nbsp;</P>', 'CONG TY CHI THANH V.N CHINH THUC DUOC CHUNG NHAN va CONG BO HOP QUY MU BAO HIEM CHITA-OMONO-SAFE\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ngay sau khi Quyet dinh so 04/2008 cua Bo Khoa hoc-Cong nghe&nbsp; trien khai thuc hien quy chuan Viet Nam 2008 ve chung nhan cong bo hop quy, gan tem chuan CR thay the cho tem CS duoc ban hanh, Ban giam doc CTY CHI THANH V.N da khan truong chi dao Bo phan ky thuat nghien cuu tim hiem quy chuan moi, len ke hoach dieu chinh khuon mau va quy trinh cong nghe san xuat de di dau trong cong cuoc cai tien, nang cap chat luong san pham theo chi dao cua Bo .\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khong ngung nghien cuu, khong ngung sang tao, ngay 25/09/2008 CTY CHI THANH V.N chinh thuc duoc TRUNG TAM TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG 03-QUATEST 3 quyet dinh chung nhan hop quy cho mot so mau san pham Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE. Ngay sau khi hoan thanh thu tuc chung nhan, ho so cong bo hop quy cua CTY CHI THANH V.N duoc goi den CHI CUC TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG - TP.HCM de thuc hien cong bo hop quy. \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ngay 06/10/2008, CHI CUC T