(5, 100, 2, 'Chat luong mu bao hiem: Khong kiem soat duoc!', '', 'CHAT LUONG MU BAO HIEM KHONG KIEM SOAT DUOC\r\nTT - Xung quanh van de chat luong mu bao hiem, ong Hoang Lam - pho giam doc Trung tam Ky thuat tieu chuan do luong chat luong 3 - cho biet: \r\n- Rat kho danh gia day du ve chat luong cac loai MBH tren thi truong vi nguon goc MBH rat da dang. Co loai san xuat trong nuoc, loai nhap khau theo duong chinh ngach co kiem soat va ca loai khong ro nguon goc.&nbsp;', '', 'CHAT LUONG MU BAO HIEM KHONG KIEM SOAT DUOC\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCac co quan chuc nang khong kiem soat duoc chat luong mu bao hiem thi nguoi dan biet chon lua loai mu nao cho an toan? Trong anh: chon mua mu bao hiem tai ben pha Binh Khanh de di huyen Can Gio, TP.HCM TT - Xung quanh van de chat luong mu bao hiem, ong Hoang Lam - pho giam doc Trung tam Ky thuat tieu chuan do luong chat luong 3 - cho biet:\r\n- Rat kho danh gia day du ve chat luong cac loai MBH tren thi truong vi nguon goc MBH rat da dang. Co loai san xuat trong nuoc, loai nhap khau theo duong chinh ngach co kiem soat va ca loai khong ro nguon goc.&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\nMBH nhap khau theo duong chinh thuc kha da dang va tu nhieu nguon nhu Thai Lan, Malaysia, Han Quoc, Trung Quoc... duoc kiem tra chat luong va dan tem kiem tra. Theo qui dinh, neu chat luong MBH qua kiem tra khong dat yeu cau se bi tai xuat hoac huy bo. Con MBH nhap khau khong chinh thuc hoac nhap lau thi khong kiem soat duoc nen van de chat luong cua nhom nay can phai duoc quan tam. \r\nDoi voi MBH san xuat trong nuoc, theo qui dinh chat luong MBH phai phu hop voi yeu cau tai tieu chuan TCVN 5756: 2005. Cac nha san xuat co the yeu cau thu nghiem tai phong thi nghiem co du nang luc va duoc cong nhan de xac dinh chat luong MBH. Sau do, nha san xuat phai cong bo phu hop voi tieu chuan tai chi cuc tieu chuan do luong o dia phuong. Tuy vay, hien trang phap ly cua nhieu loai mu dang duoc bay ban tren thi truong la khong ro rang. Dieu nay cho thay viec kiem tra MBH tren thi truong chua duoc thuc hien nghiem tuc va co the noi la rat thieu kiem soat. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTheo Uy ban An toan giao thong quoc gia, den cuoi nam 2006 ca nuoc co hon 18,4 trieu moto, xe gan may (so voi nam 2005 tang 14,1%, binh quan moi nam gan day ca nuoc dang ky moi tu 2-2,5 trieu moto, xe gan may). Neu tinh binh quan it nhat mot moto, gan may co hai nguoi su dung MBH thi ca nuoc&nbsp; can khoang 40 trieu MBH. * Tai sao khong kiem soat duoc chat luong MBH, thua ong?\r\n- Theo quyet dinh 50 cua Thu tuong Chinh phu, viec kiem tra chat luong MBH nhap khau va san xuat trong nuoc duoc chi dinh cho cac trung tam ky thuat tieu chuan do luong chat luong 1, 2, 3 va cac to chuc ky thuat khac thuc hien. Tuy nhien, cac don vi nay chi duoc chi dinh thuc hien theo yeu cau cua cac co quan quan ly. Viec kiem tra, giam sat doi voi cac don vi san xuat trong nuoc va tren thi truong thuoc quyen han cua cac co quan quan ly. Mot so qui dinh con chua phu hop voi thuc te va co che quan ly thieu chat che la mot phan nguyen nhan cua tinh trang nay.\r\n* Hien co nhieu loai MBH kem chat luong bay ban tren thi truong va co noi bay ban MBH tre em duoi dang do choi? \r\n- Can phai noi ro: MBH khong phai la do choi tre em. Hien nay co nhieu doanh nghiep nhap khau co the da nup duoi dang nhap khau do choi hay MBH danh cho nguoi di xe dap de ne kiem tra. Day co the la mot ke ho vi Nha nuoc chua co qui dinh nao ve tieu chuan MBH danh cho nguoi di xe dap cung nhu chua qui dinh ve viec kiem tra chat luong voi cac loai san pham nay. \r\n* Thua ong, lam the nao de giup nguoi tieu dung chon duoc MBH dat chat luong?\r\n- Khi ba con mua MBH san xuat trong nuoc hoac MBH nhap khau can xem cac thong tin chi tiet duoc in tren nhan va bao bi voi day du noi dung: ten san pham, ten va dia chi co so san xuat, co mu va ngay, thang, nam san xuat. Doi voi MBH nhap khau phai co tem kiem tra (cua trung tam ky thuat tieu chuan do luong chat luong 1, 2 hoac 3) va MBH san xuat trong nuoc phai co dau hieu cong bo chat luong (CS).&nbsp; \r\nMot bien phap khac rat kha thi la cac nha san xuat tien hanh chung nhan san pham phu hop voi tieu chuan. Qua do san pham (MBH) duoc chung nhan se mang dau chung nhan la mot dau hieu nguoi tieu dung co the nhan biet. Thong qua viec chung nhan san pham, san pham MBH se duoc co quan chung nhan giam sat chat luong trong suot qua trinh mang dau chat luong. Trung tam ky thuat tieu chuan do luong chat luong la mot trong nhung co quan thuc hien chung nhan doi voi san pham duoc cong nhan tai VN. \r\nNGOC AN thuc hien-bao TUOI TRE(07/07/07)', '', '', 0, 1185593625, '60aa1518bf5b08c7e48efc9f5096846d'),
(76, 67, 2, 'TDNS-2010', '', 'TH&Ocirc;NG TIN TUYEN DUNG \r\nTh&aacute;ng 2/2010\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De cung co v&agrave;&nbsp;day manh&nbsp;ph&aacute;t trien&nbsp;hoat dong san xuat, kinh doanh nam 2010, CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tuyen dung nh&acirc;n su cho&nbsp;nhieu vi tr&iacute; voi muc luong thoa thuan, cu the nhu sau:\r\n\r\nXem th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin theo duong link duoi d&acirc;y:\r\nhttp://www.timviecnhanh.com/vieclam/congty/2280853/43385/cty-tnhh-sx-tm-nhua-chi-thanh-v-n.html\r\nLi&ecirc;n he&nbsp;nop&nbsp;don xin viec tai : PH&Ograve;NG NH&Acirc;N SU - CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N&nbsp;\r\nDia chi: 122 v&agrave;nh Dai Trong, phuong B&igrave;nh Tri D&ocirc;ng B, Q.B&igrave;nh T&acirc;n, Tp.HCM\r\nHan ch&oacute;t nhan ho so : 09/3/2010', '<p>test</p>', 'TH&Ocirc;NG TIN TUYEN DUNG \r\nTh&aacute;ng 2/2010\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De cung co v&agrave;&nbsp;day manh&nbsp;ph&aacute;t trien&nbsp;hoat dong san xuat, kinh doanh nam 2010, CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tuyen dung nh&acirc;n su cho&nbsp;nhieu vi tr&iacute; voi muc luong thoa thuan, cu the nhu sau:\r\n\r\n    \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            STT\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Vi tr&iacute; tuyen dung\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            So luong(Nguoi)\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Y&ecirc;u cau\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            M&ocirc; ta c&ocirc;ng viec\r\n            \r\n        \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Quan Doc\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            3 \r\n            \r\n            \r\n            - Tot nghiep c&aacute;c truong Dai Hoc, Cao Dang &hellip; (Uu ti&ecirc;n khoi ky thuat)\r\n            - C&oacute; kinh nghiepm trong linh vuc SX san pham nhua c&ocirc;ng nghiep.\r\n            - C&oacute; kha nang l&atilde;nh dao, c&oacute; tinh than tr&aacute;ch nhiem v&agrave; chiu duoc &aacute;p luc c&ocirc;ng viec\r\n            - C&oacute; &iacute;t nhat 2 nam kinh nghiem o vi tr&iacute; tuong duong.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            - Dieu h&agrave;nh c&aacute;c hoat dong SX trong nh&agrave; m&aacute;y \r\n            - Lap ke hoach SX, ke hoach bao tr&igrave;, bao duong m&aacute;y m&oacute;c\r\n            - Chiu tr&aacute;ch nhiem SX san pham d&uacute;ng ke hoach, dam bao chat luong \r\n            - Nghi&ecirc;n cuu c&aacute;c giai ph&aacute;p hieu qua de giam thieu chi ph&iacute; SX\r\n            - Dieu h&agrave;nh doi ngu c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n v&agrave; c&aacute;n bo truc thuoc nh&agrave; m&aacute;y\r\n            - Chiu tr&aacute;ch nhiem an to&agrave;n trong nh&agrave; m&aacute;y\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Ky su co kh&iacute;, bao tr&igrave; dien dien tu.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            5\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep c&aacute;c truong Dai Hoc, Cao Dang ve khoi ky thuat.\r\n            C&oacute; kinh nghiep trong viec bao h&agrave;nh v&agrave; sua chua m&aacute;y (m&aacute;y san xuat c&aacute;c san pham nhua)\r\n            C&oacute; tinh than hoc hoc hoi v&agrave; chiu &aacute;p luc cao trong c&ocirc;ng viec.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bao tr&igrave; bao duong v&agrave; sua chua m&aacute;y san xuat c&aacute;c san pham nhua.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quan l&yacute; d&agrave;o tao c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n, to co dien trong viec van h&agrave;nh m&aacute;y.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tham gia de xuat c&aacute;c cai tien ve ky thuat v&agrave; quan l&yacute; trong linh vuc ky thuat.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            C&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n l&agrave;m nguoi khu&ocirc;n mau.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            5\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep trung hoc co so tro l&ecirc;n.\r\n            C&oacute; kinh nghiem l&agrave;m nguoi khu&ocirc;n mau.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; L&agrave;m nguoi c&aacute;c loai khu&ocirc;n mau &eacute;p nhua.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thuc hien c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng viec do c&ocirc;ng ty ph&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n van h&agrave;nh m&aacute;y CNC.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            3\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep trung cap co kh&iacute; che tao m&aacute;y tro l&ecirc;n.\r\n            C&oacute; kinh nghiem van h&agrave;nh m&aacute;y CNC (uu ti&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ung vi&ecirc;n d&atilde; l&agrave;m qua ng&agrave;nh co kh&iacute; khu&ocirc;n mau)\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Van h&agrave;nh m&aacute;y CNC de che tao khu&ocirc;n mau.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thuc hien c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng viec do c&ocirc;ng ty ph&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Quan l&yacute; kinh doanh ng&agrave;nh h&agrave;ng\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            5\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep dai hoc tro l&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh ve kinh te.\r\n            C&oacute; kinh nghiep kinh doanh c&aacute;c mat h&agrave;ng nhua c&ocirc;ng nghiep \r\n            C&oacute; kha nang l&atilde;nh dao, c&oacute; tinh than tr&aacute;ch nhiem v&agrave; chiu duoc &aacute;p luc c&ocirc;ng viec\r\n            C&oacute; &iacute;t nhat 2 nam kinh nghiem o vi tr&iacute; tuong duong.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thiet lap he thong ph&acirc;n phoi cho c&aacute;c mat h&agrave;ng.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nghi&ecirc;n cuu thi truong de de ra c&aacute;c chien luoc, ke hoach kinh doanh ph&ugrave; hop.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To chuc, d&agrave;o tao v&agrave; van h&agrave;nh bo m&aacute;y kinh doanh de thuc hien d&uacute;ng theo chien luoc v&agrave; ke hoach kinh doanh cua c&ocirc;ng ty.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n nghi&ecirc;n cuu ph&aacute;t trien.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            2\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep dai hoc tro l&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh kinh te.\r\n            C&oacute; kha nang tong hop, ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch v&agrave; du b&aacute;o duoc t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh kinh te, t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thi truong.\r\n            C&oacute; kha nang nghi&ecirc;n cuu thi truong.\r\n            C&oacute; kha nang x&acirc;y dung ke hoach chi tiet cho viec ph&aacute;t trien san pham, ph&aacute;t trien thi truong.\r\n            C&oacute; the su dung c&aacute;c phan mem phuc vu cho c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c nghi&ecirc;n cuu thong k&ecirc;, du b&aacute;o (Excel, SPSS &hellip;)\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thong k&ecirc;, ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch v&agrave; du b&aacute;o t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh thi truong, xu huong ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; X&acirc;y dung ke hoach chi tiet cho viec nghi&ecirc;n cuu v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trien thi truong, san pham, phuong thuc kinh doanh, phuong thuc to chuc thuc hien.\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n thong k&ecirc; tong hop.\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            1\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            Tot nghiep trung cap tro l&ecirc;n.\r\n            Trung thuc, can than v&agrave; c&oacute; do ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c cao.\r\n            C&oacute; kha nang su dung c&aacute;c phan mem van ph&ograve;ng (Word, Excel, PowerPoint &hellip;)\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tong hop thong k&ecirc; t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh kinh doanh.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thong k&ecirc; don dat h&agrave;ng.\r\n            -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lap c&aacute;c b&aacute;o c&aacute;o ve t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh kinh doanh trong ng&agrave;y, th&aacute;ng, qu&yacute;, nam.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n    \r\n\r\nXem th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin theo duong link duoi d&acirc;y:\r\nhttp://www.timviecnhanh.com/vieclam/congty/2280853/43385/cty-tnhh-sx-tm-nhua-chi-thanh-v-n.html\r\nLi&ecirc;n he&nbsp;nop&nbsp;don xin viec tai : PH&Ograve;NG NH&Acirc;N SU - CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N&nbsp;\r\nDia chi: 122 v&agrave;nh Dai Trong, phuong B&igrave;nh Tri D&ocirc;ng B, Q.B&igrave;nh T&acirc;n, Tp.HCM\r\nHan ch&oacute;t nhan ho so : 09/3/2010\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1271254447, 'ibl33gl1d599291fr5upa3e8u5'),
(79, 50, 2, 'Qui dinh moi', '', 'Cho tre em kh&ocirc;ng doi mu bao hiem bi phat 200.000 dong\r\n\r\nTu 20/5 nguoi lon cho tre em tr&ecirc;n 6 tuoi kh&ocirc;ng doi mu bao hiem hoac  kh&ocirc;ng c&agrave;i d&acirc;y se bi phat 100.000 den 200.000 dong.\r\n\r\nD&acirc;y l&agrave; noi dung nghi dinh 34 vua duoc Thu tuong k&yacute;  ban h&agrave;nh. So voi nghi dinh 176 truoc d&acirc;y, hau het muc phat deu cao hon nham tang  t&iacute;nh ran de.', '', 'Cho tre em kh&ocirc;ng doi mu bao hiem bi phat 200.000 dong\r\n\r\nTu 20/5 nguoi lon cho tre em tr&ecirc;n 6 tuoi kh&ocirc;ng doi mu bao hiem hoac  kh&ocirc;ng c&agrave;i d&acirc;y se bi phat 100.000 den 200.000 dong.\r\n\r\nD&acirc;y l&agrave; noi dung nghi dinh 34 vua duoc Thu tuong k&yacute;  ban h&agrave;nh. So voi nghi dinh 176 truoc d&acirc;y, hau het muc phat deu cao hon nham tang  t&iacute;nh ran de.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNguoi di xe m&aacute;y bi phat den 200.000 dong neu cho th&ecirc;m  2 nguoi, tru truong hop cho nguoi benh cap cuu, tre em duoi 14 tuoi, &aacute;p giai  nguoi c&oacute; h&agrave;nh vi vi pham ph&aacute;p luat. Muc phat n&agrave;y d&atilde; tang gap d&ocirc;i so voi quy dinh  truoc d&acirc;y v&agrave; do tuoi tre em duoc cho k&egrave;m truoc kia l&agrave; tu 7 tuoi tro xuong, nay  l&agrave; 14 tuoi tro xuong.\r\nNguoi dieu khien &ocirc;t&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng chap h&agrave;nh hieu lenh cua  d&egrave;n t&iacute;n hieu giao th&ocirc;ng bi phat 600.000-800.000 dong, trong khi muc phat truoc  d&acirc;y chi 200.000&ndash;400.000 dong.\r\nNguoi l&aacute;i &ocirc;t&ocirc; chuyen l&agrave;n duong kh&ocirc;ng d&uacute;ng noi cho  ph&eacute;p hoac kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; t&iacute;n hieu b&aacute;o truoc, quay dau xe tai noi cam, tr&ecirc;n phan duong  d&agrave;nh cho nguoi di bo qua duong, bam c&ograve;i, r&uacute; ga li&ecirc;n tuc hoac bam c&ograve;i hoi, su  dung d&egrave;n chieu xa trong khu d&ocirc; thi&hellip; se bi phat toi 500.000, cao hon 2,5 lan so  voi muc phat cu.\r\nTai c&aacute;c d&ocirc; thi dac biet (H&agrave; Noi v&agrave; TP HCM) muc phat  doi voi mot so h&agrave;nh vi se tang 40-200% so voi muc chung cua ca nuoc. Cu the,  nguoi di xe m&aacute;y kh&ocirc;ng chap h&agrave;nh hieu lenh cua d&egrave;n t&iacute;n hieu giao th&ocirc;ng, di nguoc  chieu v&agrave;o duong mot chieu bi phat 300.000- 500.000 dong (muc chung  100.000-200.000 dong) v&agrave; tuoc giay ph&eacute;p l&aacute;i xe 30 ng&agrave;y.\r\nDoi voi &ocirc;t&ocirc;, c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi dung do, quay dau xe kh&ocirc;ng  d&uacute;ng quy dinh bi phat 600.000-1 trieu dong (tang gap d&ocirc;i so voi muc chung). H&agrave;nh  vi vuot d&egrave;n do, l&aacute;i &ocirc;t&ocirc; khi c&oacute; nong do con vuot muc cho ph&eacute;p se bi xu phat 1-1,4  trieu dong (muc chung l&agrave; 600.000-800.000 dong). H&agrave;nh vi di kh&ocirc;ng d&uacute;ng phan duong  hoac l&agrave;n duong quy dinh bi phat 1-1,4 trieu dong (muc chung l&agrave; 600.000-800.000  dong)&hellip;\r\nThu truong Bo Giao th&ocirc;ng Van tai Nguyen Hong Truong  cho biet, muc phat moi voi H&agrave; Noi v&agrave; TP HCM se duoc thuc hien th&iacute; diem trong 36  th&aacute;ng. Sau khi ket th&uacute;c th&iacute; diem, Bo Giao th&ocirc;ng Van tai, Bo C&ocirc;ng an, UBND H&agrave;  Noi, TP HCM se tong hop, d&aacute;nh gi&aacute; v&agrave; de xuat Ch&iacute;nh phu chu truong thuc hien tiep  theo.\r\nNghi dinh c&oacute; hieu luc tu 20/5.\r\nTheo Dat Viet', '', 'd0e93_1271919157.jpg', 1, 1271919157, 'fceb028fe49cd61a93e1fdf540400366'),
(80, 49, 2, '20 doanh nghiep doat giai ''Tiep thi sang tao'' tai hoi cho', '', '&nbsp;\r\n20 doanh nghiep doat giai &quot;Tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao&quot; tai hoi cho\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSau 6 ng&agrave;y hoi cho HVNCLC 2010 tai TP.HCM, Ban gi&aacute;m khao d&atilde; ghi nhan 20 doanh nghiep c&oacute; nhung tien bo dong deu v&agrave; noi troi...\r\nTheo d&aacute;nh gi&aacute; cua Ban to chuc, nam nay, da so c&aacute;c doanh nghiep deu c&oacute; no luc doi moi h&igrave;nh anh, dua ra nhieu san pham moi v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch chi&ecirc;u thi, khuyen m&atilde;i moi hap d&acirc;n nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng. Voi no luc deu khap d&oacute;, hoi cho d&atilde; the hien mot mat bang moi ve dang cap tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao cua tap hop c&aacute;c doanh nghiep HVNCLC cua ca nuoc. De bieu duong v&agrave; ghi nhan su no luc x&acirc;y dung thuong hieu kh&ocirc;ng ngung cua c&aacute;c doanh nghiep, BTC d&atilde; moi c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia thuong hieu, tiep thi c&oacute; cuoc khao s&aacute;t v&agrave; cham diem c&aacute;c hoat dong tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao cua c&aacute;c gian h&agrave;ng tai Hoi cho.', '', '&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n20 doanh nghiep doat giai &quot;Tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao&quot; tai hoi cho\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSau 6 ng&agrave;y hoi cho HVNCLC 2010 tai TP.HCM, Ban gi&aacute;m khao d&atilde; ghi nhan 20 doanh nghiep c&oacute; nhung tien bo dong deu v&agrave; noi troi...\r\nTheo d&aacute;nh gi&aacute; cua Ban to chuc, nam nay, da so c&aacute;c doanh nghiep deu c&oacute; no luc doi moi h&igrave;nh anh, dua ra nhieu san pham moi v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch chi&ecirc;u thi, khuyen m&atilde;i moi hap d&acirc;n nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng. Voi no luc deu khap d&oacute;, hoi cho d&atilde; the hien mot mat bang moi ve dang cap tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao cua tap hop c&aacute;c doanh nghiep HVNCLC cua ca nuoc. De bieu duong v&agrave; ghi nhan su no luc x&acirc;y dung thuong hieu kh&ocirc;ng ngung cua c&aacute;c doanh nghiep, BTC d&atilde; moi c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia thuong hieu, tiep thi c&oacute; cuoc khao s&aacute;t v&agrave; cham diem c&aacute;c hoat dong tiep thi s&aacute;ng tao cua c&aacute;c gian h&agrave;ng tai Hoi cho. \r\nBGK d&atilde; ghi nhan 20 doanh nghiep c&oacute; nhung tien bo dong deu v&agrave; noi troi ve c&aacute;c mat:&nbsp; (1) Chon v&agrave; dua ra th&ocirc;ng diep v&agrave; &yacute; tuong xuy&ecirc;n suot nhat qu&aacute;n xuat sac cho to&agrave;n bo dot hoat dong; (2) To chuc c&aacute;c hoat dong k&iacute;ch hoat hap dan v&agrave; c&oacute; t&iacute;nh chuy&ecirc;n nghiep cao tai gian h&agrave;ng; (3) Thiet ke tong the dac sac, trung b&agrave;y san pham v&agrave; hoat dong duoc huan luyen v&agrave; cham s&oacute;c tot cua doi ngu; (4) Dac biet cho ri&ecirc;ng chuy&ecirc;n de &ldquo;San pham moi &ndash; No luc cua Doanh nghiep HVNCLC v&igrave; nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng&rdquo;, doanh nghiep cung the hien su dau tu c&ocirc;ng phu cho viec t&aacute;i dinh vi, doi moi thuong hieu.\r\nDanh s&aacute;ch 20 doanh nghiep duoc chon gom: Nhua Ch&iacute; Th&agrave;nh V.N, Minh Long I, Nhon H&ograve;a, Nhua Duy T&acirc;n, Co son Thanh B&igrave;nh, Hong H&agrave;, Thi&ecirc;n Long, Nguy&ecirc;n T&acirc;m &ndash; Foci, My pham S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &ndash; SCC, PNJ, Duoc Hau Giang, Acecook Viet Nam, Nhua Rang D&ocirc;ng (Rando), Hy L&acirc;m M&ocirc;n, Ladofood, Nestle, Vinh Tien (tap), SG. Fisco, Li&ecirc;n Th&agrave;nh, Biti&rsquo;s.&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1272964353, '178b28ffd17369ac64a0a6562c7275dc'),
(7, 97, 2, 'Nhan biet non bao hiem OMONO', '', 'NHAN BIET\r\nNOÌN BAO HIEM OMONO THAÌ£T \r\n&nbsp;\r\nVaÌ€o ngaÌ€y 19 thaÌng 07 nam 2007 , Cau LaÌ£c BoÌ£ ChoÌng HaÌ€ng GiaÌ‰ vaÌ€ chuong triÌ€nh KieÌn ThuÌc Tieu DuÌ€ng cuÌ‰a daÌ€i truyeÌ€n hiÌ€nh HTV7 daÌƒ coÌ moÌ£t buoÌ‰i laÌ€m vieÌ£c voÌi CONG TY CHIÌ THAÌ€NH V.N deÌ‰ giaÌ‰i daÌp thaÌc maÌc cuÌ‰a nguoÌ€i tieu duÌ€ng veÌ€ vaÌn deÌ€ noÌn baÌ‰o hieÌ‰m nhaÌy vaÌ€ giaÌ‰ thuong hieÌ£u OMONO cuÌ‰a CONG TY CHIÌ THAÌ€NH V.N. Chuong trinh nay da duoc phat song vao luc 2h15 phut ngay 22/07/07 va duoc phat lai luc 11h30 ngay 23/07/07.', '', 'NHAN BIET \r\nNOÌN BAO HIEM OMONO THAÌ£T \r\n&nbsp;\r\nVaÌ€o ngaÌ€y 19 thaÌng 07 nam 2007 , Cau LaÌ£c BoÌ£ ChoÌng HaÌ€ng GiaÌ‰ vaÌ€ chuong triÌ€nh KieÌn ThuÌc Tieu DuÌ€ng cuÌ‰a daÌ€i truyeÌ€n hiÌ€nh HTV7 daÌƒ coÌ moÌ£t buoÌ‰i laÌ€m vieÌ£c voÌi CONG TY CHIÌ THAÌ€NH V.N deÌ‰ giaÌ‰i daÌp thaÌc maÌc cuÌ‰a nguoÌ€i tieu duÌ€ng veÌ€ vaÌn deÌ€ noÌn baÌ‰o hieÌ‰m nhaÌy vaÌ€ giaÌ‰ thuong hieÌ£u OMONO cuÌ‰a CONG TY CHIÌ THAÌ€NH V.N. Chuong trinh nay da duoc phat song vao luc 2h15 phut ngay 22/07/07 va duoc phat lai luc 11h30 ngay 23/07/07.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp;\r\nMC NgoÌ£c Nga daÌƒ doÌ£c thu thaÌc maÌc cuÌ‰a chiÌ£ TraÌ€n ThiÌ£ Tam, ngu tai so 611/575A duong Dien Bien Phu, Q.3, Tp.HCM .Trong thu ChiÌ£ Tam theÌ‰ hieÌ£n suÌ£ hoang mang veÌ€ vieÌ£c laÌ€m sao deÌ‰ phan bieÌ£t duoÌ£c dau laÌ€ nhaÌƒn hieÌ£u NoÌn BaÌ‰o HieÌ‰m thaÌ£t, coÌ dang kyÌ nhaÌƒn hieÌ£u haÌ€ng hoÌa cuÌƒng nhu daÌ‰m baÌ‰o chaÌt luoÌ£ng vaÌ€ daÌng tin caÌ£y. DaÌ£i dieÌ£n CONG TY CHIÌ THAÌ€NH V.N, ong HOÌ€ LE PHONG â€“ PhuÌ£ traÌch kyÌƒ thuaÌ£t daÌƒ giaÌ‰i daÌp cuÌ£ theÌ‰ cho chiÌ£ Tam nhu sau:\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp; â€œ ''Thu nhat : Hien nay, tren thi truong nhung nhan hieu non bao hiem co canh phat am gan giong nhau nhu truong hop chi Tam thac mac rat nhieu, vi du nhu : OMONO, AMORO, AMARO,AMONOâ€¦vv trong do that - gia lan lon. Xin tra loi Chi Tam la non bao hiem mang nhan hieu â€œOMONOâ€ do CONG TY NHUA CHI THANH V.N san xuat va dua ra luu hanh tren thi truong da duoc cap giay phep dang ky nhan hieu hang hoa so : 68649 do CUC SO HUU TRI TUE cap ngay : 09/12/2005 va duoc bao ho tren thi truong Viet Nam\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thu hai : Cac mau non bao hiem mang nhan hieu OMONO do CONG TY CHI THANH V.N san xuat deu dat tieu chuan : TCVN 5756:2001 do TRUNG TAM KY THUAT 1 thuoc TONG CUC TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG kiem dinh va chung nhan.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thu ba : Tren thi truong hien nay da xuat hien mot so mu bao hiem nhay va gia thuong hieu OMONO gay nham lan cho nguoi tieu dung.Thong qua chuong trinh â€œKien Thuc Tieu Dungâ€ hom nay, toi xin huong dan nguoi tieu dung cach nhan biet Non bao hiem â€œOMONOâ€ that cua chung toi qua nhung dac diem cu the nhu sau : \r\n&nbsp;\r\n1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Non bao hiem mang nhan hieu OMONO co logo cua Cong ty CHI THANH V.N noi len duoi luoi trai cua non non\r\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Phia sau non co dan tem kiem dinh (Tem CS) co ten CONG TY NHUA CHI THANH V.N\r\n3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vai lot ben trong nhan min, khong gay di ung , day quai va khoa non chac chan, an toan . Tat ca nhung phu kien san xuat non duoc san xuat bang chat lieu cao cap, khi tiep xuc co cam giac rat khac biet voi hang nhay.\r\n4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lop nuoc son phu tren non day, nhan bong va co do chiu nhiet cao khong bi nhat mau theo thoi gian.\r\n5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Cong Ty NHUA CHI THANH V.N da duoc cap chung chi ISO 9001:2000 nen toan bo qui trinh san xuat cua chung toi duoc kiem soat rat chat che.Tat ca non bao hiem deu duoc kiem tra chat luong mot cach nghiem tuc truoc khi dua ra thi truong nham dam bao an toan tuyet doi cho nguoi tieu dung khi su dung.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Ngoai ra, truong hop co nghi van hang that-hang gia-hang nhay hay thac mac ve mu bao hiem â€œOMONOâ€ nguoi tieu dung co the lien he tai dia chi :\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CONG TY NHUA CHI THANH V.N \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dia chi: 415 B, duong Kinh Duong Vuong, P12, Q.6, Tp.HCM \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dien thoai: 08 8750 310&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Email : contact@chithanhvn.com&nbsp; de duoc huong dan giai quyet .â€\r\n&nbsp;', '', 'mc _1185152251.jpg', 1, 1191858358, '97f6373817cc29eb4fe0a36dfa5fcd63');
INSERT INTO `tb_content` (`id`, `sort`, `cat_id`, `title`, `title_en`, `short_body`, `short_body_en`, `long_body`, `long_body_en`, `file1`, `active`, `time`, `sid`) VALUES
(10, 96, 2, 'OMONO hay AMONO', '', '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; OMONO hay AMONO \r\n&nbsp;\r\nNgay 20/09/2007 vua qua TONG CUC TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG da cong bo danh sach nhan hieu mu bao hiem da thuc cong bo phu hop tieu chuan TCVN 5756:2001 de giup nguoi tieu dung ca nuoc co quyet dinh dung dan trong viec chon mua mu bao hiem cung nhu giup cac nha san xuat tranh duoc su nhap nhang thuong hieu, that gia lan lon cua thi truong mu bao hiem hien nay. Nhung do co mot so sai sot nen da cong bo khong chinh xac nhan hieu non bao hiem cua CONG TY TNHH SX-TM NHUA CHI THANH V.N san xuat , dieu nay da gay xon xao du luan,&nbsp; anh huong rat nhieu den uy tin thuong hieu cua CONG TY CHI THANH V.N. La mot nha san xuat non bao hiem co danh tieng tren thi truong trong nhieu nam qua, CONG TY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp; da duoc nguoi tieu dung ca nuoc biet den va tin dung qua cac nhung chiec mu bao hiem chat luong mang cac nhan hieu : CHITA, OMONO, REBEL\r\n&nbsp;\r\nTONG CUC TRUONG-TONG CUC TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG Ong NGO QUY VIET da ghi nhan dieu nay nen vao ngay &nbsp;28/09/07 , ong da cho ban hanh cong van cai chinh goi den cac co quan thong tin dai chung cai chinh lai nhu sau: Mu bao hiem do CONG TY TNHH SX-TM NHUA CHI THANH V.N san xuat, mang nhan hieu OMONO da cong bo phu hop tieu chuan.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', '', '', 1, 1191858180, '8m4stuidtiodjnni6t0pshk2h5'),
(13, 100, 2, 'MOT CHIEC MU BAO HIEM CO 4 LOAI TEM', '', 'MOT CHIEC MU BAO HIEM CO 4&nbsp;LOAI TEM \r\nDe bao ve quyen loi cua nguoi tieu dung cung nhu bao ve uy tin thuong hieu cua cong ty, CTY CHI THANH V.N khong nhung khong ngung hoan thien mau ma, nang cao chat luong san pham ma con luon huong toi nhung chu truong thiet thuc nham trao tay nguoi tieu dung nhung chiec mu bao hiem hoan thien nhat.', '', 'MOT CHIEC MU BAO HIEM CO 4&nbsp;LOAI TEM \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De bao ve quyen loi cua nguoi tieu dung cung nhu bao ve uy tin thuong hieu cua cong ty, CTY CHI THANH V.N khong nhung khong ngung hoan thien mau ma, nang cao chat luong san pham ma con luon huong toi nhung chu truong thiet thuc nham trao tay nguoi tieu dung nhung chiec mu bao hiem hoan thien nhat.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bat dau tu thang 11-2007, mu bao hiem do CONG TY CHI THANH V.N san xuat co&nbsp;den 4 loai tem sau day:\r\n\r\n1.Tem kiem dinh tem CS -TCVN 5756:2001\r\n2.Tem chong hang gia do Vien Khoa Hoc Hinh Su-Bo Cong An phat hanh\r\n3.Tem bao hiem trach nhihem san pham tri gia 2.5 ty cua CTY BAO HIEM PJICO\r\n4.Tem cam ket chat luong- ''bao dap'' , nha san xuat cam ket ve chat luong san pham, nguoi tieu dung co the kiem tra, dap thu&nbsp;mu neu muon.\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1195062135, '27i8e7iqqij7mm7turrgerl6i5'),
(14, 99, 2, 'CTY CHI THANH V.N CUU TRO DONG BAO MIEN TRUNG', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N CUU TRO DONG BAO MIEN TRUNG\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Truoc tinh canh Mien Trung chim trong nuoc lu, Giam doc CTY CHI THANH V.N - ong NGUYEN VAN LAP da cu dai dien lien hen voi co quan chuc nang, truc tiep den Mien Trung cuu tro dong bao dang gap kho khan.', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N CUU TRO DONG BAO MIEN TRUNG\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Truoc tinh canh Mien Trung chim trong nuoc lu, Giam doc CTY CHI THANH V.N - ong NGUYEN VAN LAP da cu dai dien lien hen voi co quan chuc nang, truc tiep den Mien Trung cuu tro dong bao dang gap kho khan.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Du kien sang ngay 17/11/2007 xe tai cho hang cuu tro cua CTY CHI THANH V.N se xuat phat di Mien Trung. Trong chuyen di nay, ngoai viec cuu tro luong thuc, thuc pham cho dong bao dang gap canh doi kho, cong ty con trao tang hoc bong va non bao hiem, trang bi cho cac em hoc sinh khuyen khich cac em tro lai hoc tap sau mua lu.\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hy vong voi su&nbsp;dong gop nay, CONG TY CHI THANH V,N co the phan nao sang se&nbsp;kho khan voi&nbsp;dong bao Mien Trung.&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1206591165, '27i8e7iqqij7mm7turrgerl6i5'),
(15, 98, 2, 'TANG NON CHO NGUOI CO THU NHAP THAP', '', 'TANG NON CHO NGUOI CO THU NHAP THAP\r\nPhoi hop voi Ban An Toan Giao Thong, Uy Ban Mat Tran Thanh Pho va Cong Ty to chuc su kien Thap Doi, vao ngay 24-25/11/2007 tai Khu du lich SUOI TIEN, CTY CHI THANH V.N da trao tang nguoi co thu nhap thap cua Tp.HCM 1.200 non bao hiem.', '', 'TANG NON CHO NGUOI CO THU NHAP THAP\r\nPhoi hop voi Ban An Toan Giao Thong, Uy Ban Mat Tran Thanh Pho va Cong Ty to chuc su kien Thap Doi, vao ngay 24-25/11/2007 tai Khu du lich SUOI TIEN, CTY CHI THANH V.N da trao tang nguoi co thu nhap thap cua Tp.HCM 1.200 non bao hiem.\r\nVoi thong&nbsp;diep ''QUAN TRONG LA CAI&nbsp;DAU'' chuong trinh mang&nbsp;y nghia&nbsp;day thiet thuc nay&nbsp;da&nbsp;duoc&nbsp;dong&nbsp;dao nguoi dan&nbsp;huong&nbsp;ung tham du.Ngoai ra,&nbsp;de gop phan xay dung&nbsp;y thuc&nbsp;tuan thu luat giao thong cung nhu tu bao ve ban than cua cac em thanh thieu nien, CTY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp;cung&nbsp;da tai tro&nbsp;non&nbsp;de cac em tham gia chuong trinh Trang tri mu bao hiem va Ve tranh ve an toan giao thong.Hoi thi&nbsp;da thu hut&nbsp;dong dao cac em tu nhieu tinh thanh tham gia soi noi.\r\nVoi nhung y nghia tich cuc nay, trong thoi gian toi, chuong trinh se tiep tuc dien ra&nbsp;o cac&nbsp;dia&nbsp;diem :&nbsp;Cong Vien Van Hoa&nbsp;Dam Sen, Cong Vien 23/9 ...&nbsp;&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1195970002, 'tis35a0r5bk3003lprm33rinm4'),
(16, 97, 2, 'NON BAO HIEM GIA NHAN HIEU CUA CTY CHI THANH V.N', '', '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;NON BAO HIEM GIA NHAN HIEU CUACTY CHI THANH V.N\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vua qua theo phan anh cua mot so dai ly ban hang ve hien tuong co mot so Mu Bao Hiem mang nhung&nbsp;nhan hieu noi tieng cua CTY CHI THANH V.N nhu : CHITA, OMONO, REBEL va SAFE dang duoc chao ban tren thi truong voi gia re bat ngo. Cong Ty da cu nhan vien di tim hieu su viec. Ket qua dieu tra cho biet&nbsp;nhung nhan&nbsp;hieu non bao hiem cua CTY CHI THANH V.N dang bi to chuc lam gia hang loat tai&nbsp;Tra Vinh.&nbsp;Dai dien cong ty&nbsp;da&nbsp;den tan&nbsp;dia phuong trinh bay su viec voi cac&nbsp;Co quan chuc nang, qua xem xet, dieu tra&nbsp;CONG AN CHAU THANH&nbsp;da goi chung toi&nbsp;Cong Van&nbsp;Phuc&nbsp;Dap duoi&nbsp;day&nbsp;:', '', '&nbsp;NON BAO HIEM GIA NHAN HIEU CUA CTY CHI THANH V.N\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vua qua theo phan anh cua mot so dai ly ban hang ve hien tuong co mot so Mu Bao Hiem mang nhung&nbsp;nhan hieu noi tieng cua CTY CHI THANH V.N nhu : CHITA, OMONO, REBEL va SAFE dang duoc chao ban tren thi truong voi gia re bat ngo. Cong Ty da cu nhan vien di tim hieu su viec. Ket qua dieu tra cho biet&nbsp;nhung nhan&nbsp;hieu non bao hiem cua CTY CHI THANH V.N dang bi to chuc lam gia hang loat tai&nbsp;Tra Vinh.&nbsp;Dai dien cong ty&nbsp;da&nbsp;den tan&nbsp;dia phuong trinh bay su viec voi cac&nbsp;Co quan chuc nang, qua xem xet, dieu tra&nbsp;CONG AN CHAU THANH&nbsp;da goi chung toi&nbsp;Cong Van&nbsp;Phuc&nbsp;Dap duoi&nbsp;day&nbsp;:\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;CONG AN CHAU THANH&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CONG HOA XA HOI CHU NGHIAVIET NAM\r\nDOI CS DTTP VE TTQLKT-CV&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Doc Lap-Tu Do-Hanh Phuc\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So : 01/2007&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Chau Thanh, ngay 25 thang 12 nam 2007\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\nCONG VAN PHUC DAP\r\n&nbsp;\r\nNgay 24/12/2007 doi CSDTTP ve TTQLKT-CV cong an Chau Thanh nhan duoc cong van xin xac nhan lo hang gia mang nhan hieu cua CTY NHUA CHI THANH. Nay doi CSKT cong an Chau Thanh co cong van tra loi nhu sau:\r\n&nbsp;\r\nVao ngay 20/11/07 Doi CSKT da tien hanh kiem tra va phat hien nha cua ong Thai The Tong ngu tai ap cay Duong-Thanh My-Chau Thanh â€“ Tra Vinh dang chua mot so luong lon (805) mu bao hiem khong ro nguon goc. Qua qua trinh xac minh lam ro doi tuong Tong thua nhan da mua mu bao hiem troi noi tren thi truong tai Tp.HCM, co chat luong kem roi chuyen ve Tra Vinh de gia cong lai bang cach dan logo vao nhung diem khuyen khuyet tren non va su dung tem (gia) cua cac thuong hieu noi tieng tren thi truong nhu Nhua Chi Thanh, nhua Lien Hiepâ€¦roi tung ra thi truong. Trong so nhung mu bao hiem thu duoc tai nha ong Thai The Tong co mu bao hiem dan tem kiem dinh CS cua Cong Ty TNHH SX-TM NHUA CHI THANH . Toan bo lo hang nay da bi cong an Chau Thanh tich thu va xu ly theo dung qui dinh cua phap luat. Nay doi CSKT cong an Chau Thanh tra loi cho Cong Ty nam ro.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; TM.DOI CSKT&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; XAC NHAN CUA BLD\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; DOI TRUONG\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (da ky)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;