(22, 99, 2, 'HOI CHO HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO-2008', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N THAM GIA HOI CHO HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO 2008\r\nTham gia Hoi Cho HVNCLC nam nay, CONG TY CHI THANH V.N da dua ra nhung chuong trinh khuyen mai that dac biet, thu hut dong dao nguoi tieu dung tham quan va mua sam. \r\n\r\n\r\nDoi MBH cu lay MBH moi, phi qui doi chi voi 50% gia tru san pham moi.\r\n\r\nGiam gia 20% cho dong san pham CHITA-OMONO\r\n\r\nGiam gia 10% phi trang tri MBH theo yeu cau.', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N THAM GIA HOI CHO HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO 2008\r\nTham gia Hoi Cho HVNCLC nam nay, CONG TY CHI THANH V.N da dua ra nhung chuong trinh khuyen mai that dac biet, thu hut dong dao nguoi tieu dung tham quan va mua sam. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDoi MBH cu lay MBH moi, phi qui doi chi voi 50% gia tri san pham moi.\r\n\r\nGiam gia 20% cho dong san pham CHITA-OMONO\r\n\r\nGiam gia 10% phi trang tri MBH theo yeu cau.\r\nCTY CHI THANH V.N thuc hien nhung chuong trinh khuyen mai dac biet nay voi mong muon tao dieu kien de nguoi tieu dung tiep can va su dung nhung&nbsp;chiec mu bao hiem dam bao tieu chi Khong Nhung An Toan ma con&nbsp;rat Thoi Trang&nbsp;, gop phan xoa diu&nbsp;di noi hoang mang cua nguoi tieu dung&nbsp;ve tinh trang Mu&nbsp;Bao Hiem&nbsp;kem chat luong&nbsp;dang tran lan tren thi truong hien nay.&nbsp; Dong thoi trong dip nay, Cong ty cung&nbsp;tham ra tham gia cuoc thi TOA SANG THUONG HIEU VANG do Bao Sai Gon Tiep Thi to chuc, voi nhung hoat dong trung bay va tiep thi san pham that soi noi.', '', 'yy_1210040236.jpg', 1, 1210038430, '0ndubshc8srdnkhr9f2qg701q3'),
(23, 98, 2, 'CTY CHI THANH V.N THAM GIA HOI CHO HANG VNCLC TAI DA NANG', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N THAM GIA HOI CHO HANG VNCLC \r\nTAI DA NANG\r\nTiep noi thanh cong tai Hoi Cho Hang Viet Nam Chat Luong Cao tai Tp.HCM, CTY CHI THANH V.N da co nhung hoat dong tiep thi san pham soi noi tai Tp.Da Nang. Trong suot ky hoi cho tu 20/05/08 den 25/05/08, hoi cho da thu hut duoc dong dao nguoi tieu dung tham quan, mua sam. San pham Mu Bao Hiem mang 3 thuong hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE cua CTY CHI THANH V.N da duoc rat nhieu nguoi tieu dung quan tam va danh gia cao ve chat luong cung nhu mau ma thoi trang', '', 'CTY CHI THANH V.N THAM GIA HOI CHO HANG VNCLC \r\nTAI DA NANG\r\nTiep noi thanh cong tai Hoi Cho Hang Viet Nam Chat Luong Cao tai Tp.HCM, CTY CHI THANH V.N da co nhung hoat dong tiep thi san pham soi noi tai Tp.Da Nang. Trong suot ky hoi cho tu 20/05/08 den 25/05/08, hoi cho da thu hut duoc dong dao nguoi tieu dung tham quan, mua sam. San pham Mu Bao Hiem mang 3 thuong hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE cua CTY CHI THANH V.N da duoc rat nhieu nguoi tieu dung quan tam va danh gia cao ve chat luong cung nhu mau ma thoi trang', '', 'chithanh_1_1212376916.jpg', 1, 1212477889, 'l7k3bj607vth3g3ogurmh16l44'),
(68, 72, 2, 'Chao mung HOI CHO HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO tai VUNG TAU', '', 'Sau nhung chuong trinh ban hang luu dong co vu cho cuoc van dong NGUOI VIET UU TIEN DUNG HANG VIET cua BO CHINH TRI do SO CONG THUONG tinh BA RIA-VUNG TAU phat dong, CTY CHI THANH V.N tiep tuc tham gia hoi cho HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO tai Vung Tau tu 20-25/12/2009&nbsp;voi nhieu chuong trinh khuyen mai hap dan cung nhieu uu dai dac biet.', '', 'Sau nhung chuong trinh ban hang luu dong co vu cho cuoc van dong NGUOI VIET UU TIEN DUNG HANG VIET cua BO CHINH TRI do SO CONG THUONG tinh BA RIA-VUNG TAU phat dong, CTY CHI THANH V.N tiep tuc tham gia hoi cho HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO tai Vung Tau tu 20-25/12/2009&nbsp;voi nhieu chuong trinh khuyen mai hap dan cung nhieu uu dai dac biet.\r\n\r\nSan pham chat luong tot, da dang mau ma ket hop voi noi dung khuyen mai hap dan, chuong trinh hoat nao soi dong, CTY CHI THANH V.N da duoc dong dao nguoi tieu dung tin nhiem, tham gia mua va tim hieu thong tin ve san pham.\r\nVoi nhieu no luc mang lai hieu&nbsp;ung tich&nbsp;cuc&nbsp;dang khich le,&nbsp;them mot lan nua&nbsp;DOI BAN HANG cua CTY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp;da&nbsp;duoc ban to chuc binh chon la&nbsp;DOI BAN HANG GIOI NHAT HOI CHO-Nganh gia dung.&nbsp;Duoc biet&nbsp;day la lan thu 3 trong nam 2009&nbsp;,&nbsp;doi ban hang cua CTY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp;dat&nbsp;duoc danh hieu nay.&nbsp;\r\nHoi cho HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG -VUNG TAU khep lai thanh cong my man. Qua hoi cho doanh nghiep co co hoi truc tiep gioi thieu san pham va khang dinh uy tin thuong hieu voi nguoi tieu dung, con nguoi tieu dung co co hoi nhan dien va tim hieu nhung san pham chinh hang, chinh hieu de cung co va mo rong kien thuc tieu dung.&nbsp; HOI CHO HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO den VUNG TAU lan dau tien da duoc don nhan rat nong nhiet , hy vong nam sau quay lai nhung doanh nghiep HANG VIET NAM CHAT LUONG CAO se co nhieu co hoi thiet lap thi truong va khang dinh minh hon.', '', 'to roi_giang sinh sau_1261801978.jpg', 1, 1262406944, 'ini37q2j33omfrde2bblp5lpv1'),
