(29, 100, 2, 'Trich bai viet dang tren bao Cong An ngay 11/10/2008', '', 'Mu bao hiem se duoc quan ly theo quy chuan QCVN 02:2008\r\n(CATP) Nhung ngay nay, cac cong ty san xuat mu bao hiem (MBH) dang tich cuc dua ra nhung san pham dat chuan gui mau den Trung tam tieu chuan do luong chat luong de thu nghiem va nhan tem chung nhan quy chuan QCVN 02:2008 do Tong cuc Do luong chat luong (Bo KH-CN) ban hanh de dua ra thi truong vao thoi gian toi. Mot so cong ty da co MBH dat QCVN 02:2008: dong san pham mang nhan hieu CHITA, OMONO, SAFE cua Cong ty Nhua Chi Thanh VN, Amoro, Protec, Honda...\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMot san pham dat tiau chuan 02-2008 cua cing ty Chi Thdnh VN vd tem chung nhan dat tiau chuan ky thuat CRTheo thong ke so bo thi hien nay ca nuoc co khoang 40 trieu MBH dang luu hanh. Tuy nhien con kha nhieu MBH khong dam bao chat luong nen thoi gian qua co khong it truong hop gap tai nan du doi MBH van bi chan thuong so nao dan den tu vong... Truoc tinh hinh do, tu ngay 15-11, cac luc luong chuc nang se kiem soat dong bo, chat che hon chat luong mu bao hiem theo quy chuan Viet Nam QCVN 02:2008. Theo do doanh nghiep chi duoc dua ra luu thong MBH dat chat luong, co nhan va dau CR. Nhan MBH toi thieu phai bao gom cac thong tin sau: ten san pham (phai co cum tu â€œMu bao hiem cho nguoi di moto, xe mayâ€); ten va dia chi co so san xuat; co mu; thang, nam san xuat hoac nhap khau, phan phoi. MBH bao dam tieu chuan ky thuat phai co chung nhan phu hop voi tieu chuan ky thuat, nghia la co chu CR hoac cong bo phu hop voi tieu chuan co chu CS. Ngoai cac tieu chuan duoc quy dinh nhu tren, cac loai MBH san xuat phai co chu vi vong dau 500 - 520mm, khoi luong tu 0,8kg den 1,5kg. Ngoai ra MBH phai co cau tao co ban theo 3 kieu dang: mu che nua dau, mu che ca dau va tai, che ca dau, tai va ham. De dat duoc QCVN 02:2008 thi MBH phai duoc kiem tra ky cang tu nguyen lieu cung nhu quy trinh san xuat, be mat ngoai cua vo MBH cung nhu cac bo phan khac phai nhan, khong co vet nut, khong co go va canh sac. Khong duoc su dung dinh tan, bu-long, dai oc, khoa quai deo co cac go va canh nhon sac. Ket cau mu phai dam bao tam nhin cua nguoi di moto, xe may trong khi su dung. MBH con phai chiu duoc do ben va dap va hap thu xung dong, do dam xuyen, do ben quai deo...\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNguoi tieu dung dan chon mua MBH chinh hang de tranh rui roDuoc biet, sap toi Bo KH-CN se co nhung van ban dua ra cac quy chuan ve MBH khong dat chat luong de cong an de phat hien, xu ly. Va mac du den thoi diem nay, Bo KH-CN chua co van ban nao â€œcam su dung mu bao hiem thoi trang, cach dieuâ€ nhung cac nha san xuat MBH thoi trang phai hieu rang san pham dat quy chuan QCVN 02:2008 thi se duoc luu hanh, nguoc lai chi dat tieu chuan thoi trang nhung kem chat luong la vi pham. Tuy nhien, Bo KH-CN cung dang ket hop voi Hoi Bao ve nguoi tieu dung lam mot nghien cuu xa hoi de tu van cho cac nha san xuat kieu dang MBH phu hop voi dieu kien khi hau, thi hieu cua nguoi Viet Nam nhung van dam bao tot chuc nang bao ve nguoi su dung. Sau khi co ket qua, co quan quan ly se tham van voi nha san xuat MBH dua ra thi truong.', '', 'Mu bao hiem se duoc quan ly theo quy chuan QCVN 02:2008\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n(Thu bay ,&nbsp; 11/10/2008, 07:33) \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMu bao hiem thoi trang dep nhung phai dam bao chat luong(CATP) Nhung ngay nay, cac cong ty san xuat mu bao hiem (MBH) dang tich cuc dua ra nhung san pham dat chuan gui mau den Trung tam tieu chuan do luong chat luong de thu nghiem va nhan tem chung nhan quy chuan QCVN 02:2008 do Tong cuc Do luong chat luong (Bo KH-CN) ban hanh de dua ra thi truong vao thoi gian toi. Mot so cong ty da co MBH dat QCVN 02:2008: dong san pham mang nhan hieu CHITA, OMONO, SAFE cua Cong ty Nhua Chi Thanh VN, Amoro, Protec, Honda...\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMot san pham dat tiau chuan 02-2008 cua cing ty Chi Thdnh VN vd tem chung nhan dat tiau chuan ky thuat CRTheo thong ke so bo thi hien nay ca nuoc co khoang 40 trieu MBH dang luu 