n, Bo KH-CN cung dang ket hop voi Hoi Bao ve nguoi tieu dung lam mot nghien cuu xa hoi de tu van cho cac nha san xuat kieu dang MBH phu hop voi dieu kien khi hau, thi hieu cua nguoi Viet Nam nhung van dam bao tot chuc nang bao ve nguoi su dung. Sau khi co ket qua, co quan quan ly se tham van voi nha san xuat MBH dua ra thi truong.', '', '', 1, 1240280921, '7jl7l9ae0ai0bqn0cd520vrq25'),
(25, 99, 2, 'Thong Bao', '', 'Thong Bao(V/v lien he phan phoi hang hoa CTY NHUA CHI THANH V.N)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gan day, theo phan hoi cua mot so khach hang o khu vuc Mien Bac va Cao Nguyen, co mot nhom nhan vien tiep thi tu xung la nhan vien cua CTY CHI THANH V.N den lien he ban hang voi nhung chuong trinh khuyen mai rat hap dan. Nhung sau khi thanh toan day du tien hang thi khach hang khong con lien he duoc voi nhung nguoi nay nua. Thay hoang mang, khach hang lien he ve VAN PHONG GIAO DICH cua CTY CHI THANH V.N de tim hieu them thong tin thi duoc biet nhung nhan vien nay la gia mao, toan bo nhung hoat dong khuyen mai cua no khong nam trong khuon kho chuong trinh khuyen mai cua CONG TY CHI THANH V.N .', '', 'Thong Bao(V/v lien he phan phoi hang hoa CTY NHUA CHI THANH V.N)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gan day, theo phan hoi cua mot so khach hang o khu vuc Mien Bac va Cao Nguyen, co mot nhom nhan vien tiep thi tu xung la nhan vien cua CTY CHI THANH V.N den lien he ban hang voi nhung chuong trinh khuyen mai rat hap dan. Nhung sau khi thanh toan day du tien hang thi khach hang khong con lien he duoc voi nhung nguoi nay nua. Thay hoang mang, khach hang lien he ve VAN PHONG GIAO DICH cua CTY CHI THANH V.N de tim hieu them thong tin thi duoc biet nhung nhan vien nay la gia mao, toan bo nhung hoat dong khuyen mai cua no khong nam trong khuon kho chuong trinh khuyen mai cua CONG TY CHI THANH V.N .&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Hien tai, CONG TY chung toi dang tien hanh dieu tra lam ro nhung su vu nay. De khach hang an tam khi lien he giao dich voi CONG TY CHI THANH V.N, chung toi goi kem duoi day danh sach Nhan Vien kinh doanh phu trach phan phoi hang hoa o tung khu vuc tren ca nuoc:\r\nKHU VUC MIEN BAC:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; NVKD: NGUYEN MINH QUAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dien thoai: 0909 672 365 - 0908 191 161\r\nKHU VUC MIEN TRUNG:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; NVKD: NGUYEN THANH PHUONG&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs