(30, 89, 2, '16 kieu Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE duoc chung nhan hop qui chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN', '16 helmet models which belong to CHITA-OMONO-SAFE brands have reached the new standard QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN', '16 kieu Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE duoc chung nhan hop qui chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN\r\nTinh den ngay 10/11/2008 CONG TY CHI THANH V.N da duoc TRUNG TAM TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG 03-QUATEST 3&nbsp;danh gia va chung nhan cho 16&nbsp;kieu Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE voi nhieu kich co va mau ma da dang. \r\n&nbsp;', '', '16 kieu Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE duoc chung nhan hop qui chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN\r\nTinh den ngay 10/11/2008 CONG TY CHI THANH V.N da duoc TRUNG TAM TIEU CHUAN DO LUONG CHAT LUONG 03-QUATEST 3&nbsp;danh gia va chung nhan cho 16&nbsp;kieu Mu Bao Hiem hieu CHITA-OMONO-SAFE voi nhieu kich co va mau ma da dang. Dat biet, trong dot nay, CONG TY CHI THANH V.N se di tien phong trong viec tung ra thi truong nhung chiec MU BAO HIEM THOI TRANG PHU HOP QUI CHUAN QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN&nbsp;, cham dut noi hoang mang cua nguoi tieu dung ve nhung chiec mu bao hiem thoi trang kem chat luong tran lan tren thi truong trong thoi gian qua. \r\nDu kien trong vai tuan toi, CONG TY CHI THANH V.N se tiep tuc dang ky chung nhan mo rong cho mot so kieu Mu Bao Hiem moi de phuc vu cho thi hieu da dang cua nhieu doi tuong khach hang.', '<P align=center><SPAN style=''FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold''><STRONG><FONT color=#990000><FONT size=3>16 helmet models which belong to CHITA-OMONO-SAFE brands have reached the new standard QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN</FONT> </FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=2><FONT size=2><FONT size=2><STRONG><SPAN style=''FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold''><FONT size=2>Till</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><B><SPAN style=''FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana''> </SPAN></B></FONT><SPAN style=''FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Ver