(33, 96, 2, 'Hoi cho Hang Viet Nam Chat luong cao 2009 tai An Giang', 'The Viet Nam high quality goods fair 2009 at An Giang province', '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Voi 26 kieu Mu Bao Hiem mang ba thuong hieu CHITA ,&nbsp;OMONO , SAFE da duoc Trung Tam Tieu Chuan Do Luong Chat Luong 3 -Quatest 3 chung nhan phu hop qui chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN,CTY NHUA CHI THANH V.N da dong hanh cung ban to chuc Hoi Cho Hang VNCLC trong tuan le hoi cho dien ra tai Tp. Long Xuyen , tinh An Giang. Tai day, chuong trinh khuyen mai giam gia va hau mai ''DOI NON CU LAY NON MOI'' cua CTY CHI THANH V.N da thu hut duoc dong dao nguoi tieu dung. Theo bao cao trong ky hoi cho nay, CTY CHI THANH V.N dat doanh so gap 4 lan du kien, hon 6.000 chiec Mu Bao Hiem chat luong cao, kieu dang thoi trang, mau sac da dang da ''chay'' hang trong ngay cuoi hoi cho.', '<STRONG>&nbsp;CHI THANH V.N CO.,LTD</STRONG> introduced 26 models of <STRONG>CHITA -OMONO -SAFE</STRONG> helmets which met <STRONG>QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN</STRONG> at The Viet Nam high quality goods fair 2009 at An Giang province.', '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Voi 26 kieu Mu Bao Hiem mang ba thuong hieu CHITA ,&nbsp;OMONO , SAFE da duoc Trung Tam Tieu Chuan Do Luong Chat Luong 3 -Quatest 3 chung nhan phu hop qui chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN,CTY NHUA CHI THANH V.N da dong hanh cung ban to chuc Hoi Cho Hang VNCLC trong tuan le hoi cho dien ra tai Tp. Long Xuyen , tinh An Giang. Tai day, chuong trinh khuyen mai giam gia va hau mai ''DOI NON CU LAY NON MOI'' cua CTY CHI THANH V.N da thu hut duoc dong dao nguoi tieu dung. Theo bao cao trong ky hoi cho nay, CTY CHI THANH V.N dat doanh so gap 4 lan du kien, hon 6.000 chiec Mu Bao Hiem chat luong cao, kieu dang thoi trang, mau sac da dang da ''chay'' hang trong ngay cuoi hoi cho.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;', '<P><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CHI THANH V.N CO.,LTD</STRONG> introduced 26 model