(34, 91, 2, 'CTY CHI THANH V.N chung nhan hop qui cho hai mau MBH co kinh chan gio', '', 'Trong thang 03/2009 CTY CHI THANH V.N da hoan tat qui trinh chung nhan va cong bo hop qui cho hai mau&nbsp;Mu bao Hiem co kinh chan gio hieu CHITA&nbsp;la : CHITA15 va CHITA17. Day la hai mau Mu Bao Hiem cao cap co kinh chan gio lam tu nhua PC chuyen dung voi nhieu tinh nang dac biet nhu la : chong tray, chong tia UV, khong vo ...vv\r\n\r\n(Luu y : De phan biet hang nhai, hang gia, tat ca&nbsp; MBH do CTY CHI THANH V.N san xuat deu co dan tem chong hang gia cua Vien Khoa Hoc Hinh Su Bo Cong An va toan bo kinh chan gio cao cap di kem san pham cua cong ty co khac logo cua cong ty de nhan dang. De tranh mua nham hang nhai,hang gia&nbsp;de nghi qui khach hang luu y nhung dac diem tren)\r\nDong hanh cung Ban to chuc hoi cho Hang VNCLC, trong ky hoi cho gioi thieu san pham tai Campuchia tu ngay 01 den ngay 05thang 04/2009, hai kieu Mu Bao Hiem CHITA 15 &amp; CHITA 17 la hai mau Mu Bao Hiem chu luc duoc day manh quang ba, gioi thieu den nguoi tieu dung . Theo thong tin thi truong, loai Mu Bao Hiem che kin ca dau, co kinh chan gio rat duoc nguoi tieu dung Campuchia ua chuong. Do vay, voi chat luong non cao cap, kieu dang thoi trang, da dang cong voi loai kinh chan gio chuyen dung co nhung tinh nang dac biet, hai kieu mu bao hiem CHITA 15 va CHITA 17 la niem tu hao cua CTY CHI THANH V.N trong dot gioi thieu san pham tai hoi cho ky nay ky nay.', '', 'Trong thang 03/2009 CTY CHI THANH V.N da hoan tat qui trinh chung nhan va cong bo hop qui cho hai mau&nbsp;Mu bao Hiem co kinh chan gio hieu CHITA&nbsp;la : CHITA15 va CHITA17. Day la hai mau Mu Bao Hiem cao cap co kinh chan gio lam tu nhua PC chuyen dung voi nhieu tinh nang dac biet nhu la : chong tray, chong tia UV, khong vo ...vv\r\n\r\n(Luu y : De phan biet hang nhai, hang gia, tat ca&nbsp; MBH do CTY CHI THANH V.N san xuat deu co dan tem chong hang gia cua Vien Khoa Hoc Hinh Su Bo Cong An va toan bo kinh chan gio cao cap di kem san pham cua cong ty co khac logo cua cong ty de nhan dang. De tranh mua nham hang nhai,hang gia&nbsp;de nghi qui khach hang luu y nhung dac diem tren)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dong hanh cung Ban to chuc hoi cho Hang VNCLC, trong ky hoi cho gioi thieu san pham tai Campuchia tu ngay 01 den ngay 05thang 04/2009, hai kieu Mu Bao Hiem CHITA 15 &amp; CHITA 17 la hai mau Mu Bao Hiem chu luc duoc day manh quang ba, gioi thieu den nguoi tieu dung . Theo thong tin thi truong, loai Mu Bao Hiem che kin ca dau, co kinh chan gio rat duoc nguoi tieu dung Campuchia ua chuong. Do vay, voi chat luong non cao cap, kieu dang thoi trang, da dang cong voi loai kinh chan gio chuyen dung co nhung tinh nang dac biet, hai kieu mu bao hiem CHITA 15 va CHITA 17 la niem tu hao cua CTY CHI THANH V.N trong dot gioi thieu san pham tai hoi cho ky nay ky nay.', '<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=''WIDTH: 635px; HEIGHT: 410px'' height=534 alt='''' hspace=0 src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/cpc_1238424452.jpg'' width=743 align=baseline border=0></P>', 'cpc_1238425152.jpg', 1, 1238425399, 'n67fskifjg8b968b9kfiel3l93'),
