(74, 70, 2, 'DOI MU BAO HIEM ...KEM CHAT LUONG CHO NONG DAN', '', 'DOI MU BAO HIEM ...KEM CHAT LUONG CHO NONG DAN\r\n\r\nTheo bao Phap Luat Tp.HCM \r\nhttp://phapluattp.vn/201001231245271p0c1015/doi-mu-bao-hiem-kem-chat-luong-cho-nong-dan.htm\r\n\r\n       \r\n           (PL)- Ngay 22-1, tai Hoi nghi so ket chuong trinh â€œDoi mu bao hiem (MBH) kem chat luong lay MBH moi dung quy chuanâ€ do Trung tam Ho tro nong dan, nong thon - Hoi Nong dan (HND) Viet Nam to chuc.\r\n\r\nDai dien HND cac tinh Lam Dong, Dong Nai, Ben Tre phan anh mot so nha cung cap thay vi doi MBH dung quy chuan lai dua MBH kem chat luong va mau ma khong dep cho nong dan. \r\n\r\nCu the, lo MBH 200 chiec mang nhan hieu ST 333 do Cong ty TNHH TM-DV Sy Tam cung cap. Lo mu nay duoc Chi cuc Tieu chuan Do luong Chat luong tinh Lam Dong kiem dinh chua dam bao chat luong. Ngoai ra, mot so lo mu khac co mau ma xau. Tai Dong Nai cung xay ra nhieu truong hop tuong tu.', '', 'DOI MU BAO HIEM ...KEM CHAT LUONG CHO NONG DAN\r\n\r\nTheo bao Phap Luat Tp.HCM \r\nhttp://phapluattp.vn/201001231245271p0c1015/doi-mu-bao-hiem-kem-chat-luong-cho-nong-dan.htm\r\n\r\n\r\n          (PL)- Ngay 22-1, tai Hoi nghi so ket chuong trinh â€œDoi mu bao hiem (MBH) kem chat luong lay MBH moi dung quy chuanâ€ do Trung tam Ho tro nong dan, nong thon - Hoi Nong dan (HND) Viet Nam to chuc.\r\n\r\n           Dai dien HND cac tinh Lam Dong, Dong Nai, Ben Tre phan anh mot so nha cung cap thay vi doi MBH dung quy chuan lai dua MBH kem chat luong va mau ma khong dep cho nong dan. \r\n\r\n           Cu the, lo MBH 200 chiec mang nhan hieu ST 333 do Cong ty TNHH TM-DV Sy Tam cung cap. Lo mu nay duoc Chi cuc Tieu chuan Do luong Chat luong tinh Lam Dong kiem dinh chua dam bao chat luong. Ngoai ra, mot so lo mu khac co mau ma xau. Tai Dong Nai cung xay ra nhieu truong hop tuong tu. \r\n\r\n           Ong Nguyen Duy Luong, Pho Chu tich HND Viet Nam, yeu cau cac dia phuong giam sat chat viec thu doi MBH, dong thoi thong ke so luong MBH kem chat luong da doi cho nguoi dan de co bien phap xu ly. \r\n\r\n           Chuong trinh thu doi MBH cho nong dan trien khai tu 2008, den nay da thu doi tren 297.000 chiec cho nong dan tai 18 tinh, thanh. Moi MBH cu dem doi duoc giam 50.000 dong. \r\n\r\nP.DIEN', '', '', 0, 1265097176, '3lagg47em36hpkrp8amouaceo0'),
(75, 100, 2, 'THONG TIN TUYEN DUNG', '', 'THONG TIN TUYEN DUNG Thang 2/2010\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De cung co va&nbsp;day manh&nbsp;phat trien&nbsp;hoat dong san xuat, kinh doanh nam 2010, CTY CHI THANH V.N thong bao tuyen dung nhan su cho&nbsp;nhieu vi tri.\r\nLien he&nbsp;nop&nbsp;don xin viec tai : PHONG NHAN SU - CTY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp;Dia chi: 122 vanh Dai Trong, phuong Binh Tri Dong B, Q.Binh Tan, Tp.HCM\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;', '', 'THONG TIN TUYEN DUNG Thang 2/2010\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De cung co va&nbsp;day manh&nbsp;phat trien&nbsp;hoat dong san xuat, kinh doanh nam 2010, CTY CHI THANH V.N thong bao tuyen dung nhan su cho&nbsp;nhieu vi tri voi muc luong thoa thuan, cu the nhu sau:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSTT\r\n\r\nVi tri tuyen dung\r\n\r\nSo luong(Nguoi)\r\n\r\nYeu cau\r\n\r\nMo ta cong viec\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nQuan Doc\r\n\r\n3 \r\n\r\n- Tot nghiep cac truong Dai Hoc, Cao Dang â€¦ (Uu tien khoi ky thuat)\r\n- Co kinh nghiepm trong linh vuc SX san pham nhua cong nghiep.\r\n- Co kha nang lanh dao, co tinh than trach nhiem va chiu duoc ap luc cong viec\r\n- Co it nhat 2 nam kinh nghiem o vi tri tuong duong.\r\n\r\n- Dieu hanh cac hoat dong SX trong nha may \r\n- Lap ke hoach SX, ke hoach bao tri, bao duong may moc\r\n- Chiu trach nhiem SX san pham dung ke hoach, dam bao chat luong \r\n- Nghien cuu cac giai phap hieu qua de giam thieu chi phi SX\r\n- Dieu hanh doi ngu cong nhan va can bo truc thuoc nha may\r\n- Chiu trach nhiem an toan trong nha may\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nKy su co khi, bao tri dien dien tu.\r\n\r\n5\r\n\r\nTot nghiep cac truong Dai Hoc, Cao Dang ve khoi ky thuat.\r\nCo kinh nghiep trong viec bao hanh va sua chua may (may san xuat cac san pham nhua)\r\nCo tinh than hoc hoc hoi va chiu ap luc cao trong cong viec.\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bao tri bao duong va sua chua may san xuat cac san pham nhua.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quan ly dao tao cong nhan, to co dien trong viec van hanh may.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tham gia de xuat cac cai tien ve ky thuat va quan ly trong linh vuc ky thuat.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCong nhan lam nguoi khuon mau.\r\n\r\n5\r\n\r\nTot nghiep trung hoc co so tro len.\r\nCo kinh nghiem lam nguoi khuon mau.\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lam nguoi cac loai khuon mau ep nhua.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thuc hien cac cong viec do cong ty phan cong.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNhan vien van hanh may CNC.\r\n\r\n3\r\n\r\nTot nghiep trung cap co khi che tao may tro len.\r\nCo kinh nghiem van hanh may CNC (uu tien cac ung vien da lam qua nganh co khi khuon mau)\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Van hanh may CNC de che tao khuon mau.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thuc hien cac cong viec do cong ty phan cong.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nQuan ly kinh doanh nganh hang\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n5\r\n\r\nTot nghiep dai hoc tro len cac nganh ve kinh te.\r\nCo kinh nghiep kinh doanh cac mat hang nhua cong nghiep \r\nCo kha nang lanh dao, co tinh than trach nhiem va chiu duoc ap luc cong viec\r\nCo it nhat 2 nam kinh nghiem o vi tri tuong duong.\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thiet lap he thong phan phoi cho cac mat hang.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nghien cuu thi truong de de ra cac chien luoc, ke hoach kinh doanh phu hop.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To chuc, dao tao va van hanh bo may kinh doanh de thuc hien dung theo chien luoc va ke hoach kinh doanh cua cong ty.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNhan vien nghien cuu phat trien.\r\n\r\n2\r\n\r\nTot nghiep dai hoc tro len cac nganh kinh te.\r\nCo kha nang tong hop, phan tich va du bao duoc tinh hinh kinh te, tinh hinh thi truong.\r\nCo kha nang nghien cuu thi truong.\r\nCo kha nang xay dung ke hoach chi tiet cho viec phat trien san pham, phat trien thi truong.\r\nCo the su dung cac phan mem phuc vu cho cong tac nghien cuu thong ke, du bao (Excel, SPSS â€¦)\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thong ke, phan tich va du bao tinh hinh thi truong, xu huong tieu dung.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Xay dung ke hoach chi tiet cho viec nghien cuu va phat trien thi truong, san pham, phuong thuc kinh doanh, phuong thuc to chuc thuc hien.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNhan vien thong ke tong hop.\r\n\r\n1\r\n\r\nTot nghiep trung cap tro len.\r\nTrung thuc, can than va co do chinh xac cao.\r\nCo kha nang su dung cac phan mem van phong (Word, Excel, PowerPoint â€¦)\r\n\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tong hop thong ke tinh hinh kinh doanh.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Thong ke don dat hang.\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lap cac bao cao ve tinh hinh kinh doanh trong ngay, thang, quy, nam.\r\nXem them thong tin theo duong link duoi day:\r\nhttp://www.timviecnhanh.com/vieclam/congty/2280853/43385/cty-tnhh-sx-tm-nhua-chi-thanh-v-n.html\r\nLien he&nbsp;nop&nbsp;don xin viec tai : PHONG NHAN SU - CTY CHI THANH V.N&nbsp;Dia chi: 122 vanh Dai Trong, phuong Binh Tri Dong B, Q.Binh Tan, Tp.HCM\r\nHan chot nhan ho so : 09/3/2010', '', '', 1, 1266918063, 'd11f4ifb60r0nupnhhhcira6g6'),
(65, 74, 2, 'DN kien nghi ''siet'' mu bao hiem kem chat luong.', '', 'TP.HCM: DN kien nghi â€œsietâ€ mu bao hiem kem chat luong\r\nBai viet cap nhat luc: 12:20 ngay 05/10/2009 \r\n\r\nMu bao hiem kem chat luong co gia ban 25.000 dong/mu duoc bay tran lan o le duong. Anh: MAI THAO\r\n(PL)- Ngay 4-10, muoi doanh nghiep san xuat mu bao hiem dong long cung ky ten vao mot ban kien nghi gui cho cac co quan quan ly nha nuoc keu cuu ve tinh trang mat hang mu bao hiem kem chat luong duoc san xuat va bay ban tran lan.', '', 'TP.HCM: DN kien nghi â€œsietâ€ mu bao hiem kem chat luong\r\nBai viet cap nhat luc: 12:20 ngay 05/10/2009 \r\n\r\nMu bao hiem kem chat luong co gia ban 25.000 dong/mu duoc bay tran lan o le duong. Anh: MAI THAO\r\n(PL)- Ngay 4-10, muoi doanh nghiep san xuat mu bao hiem dong long cung ky ten vao mot ban kien nghi gui cho cac co quan quan ly nha nuoc keu cuu ve tinh trang mat hang mu bao hiem kem chat luong duoc san xuat va bay ban tran lan.\r\nCu the, doanh nghiep kien nghi co quan quan ly hai van de. Do la can dua ngay mat hang mu bao hiem vao danh sach hang hoa san xuat, kinh doanh co dieu kien. Thu hai la chi dao cac don vi quan ly nha nuoc nhu quan ly thi truong, cong an kinh te, cac trung tam chung nhan chat luongâ€¦ triet pha, xu phat that nang cac ca nhan, to chuc san xuat mu nhai, mu kem chat luong. \r\nTrong don gui den Bo Khoa hoc va Cong nghe, Bo Cong thuong, Bo Cong an va co quan quan ly khac, cac doanh nghiep cho biet hien nay ngoai thi truong tran ngap mu bao hiem dom, mu khong co dau chat luong, khong ten, tuoi, dia chi noi san xuatâ€¦ Dac diem mu kem chat luong la coi mu lam bang nhua tai che, phan mop xop ben trong rat mong nen khong an toan cho nguoi su dung. Vi san xuat khong theo tieu chuan ky thuat nao va su dung nhua phe thai nen loai mu kem chat luong nay ban gia rat re 20.000-30.000 dong/mu.\r\nTheo www.phapluattp.vn\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1260843694, 'dcsor57hn2ob48388s60dpno25'),
(66, 73, 2, 'CHO TIN HIEU TU BO CONG THUONG', '', 'Cho tin hieu tu Bo Cong Thuong\r\nLao Dong so 283 Ngay 12/12/2009&nbsp;Cap nhat: Thu Bay, 12/12/2009 - 7:33 AM\r\n\r\n(LD) - O nuoc ta hien con mot so luong rat lon cac san pham MBH kem chat luong da va dang duoc nguoi tieu dung (NTD) mua va su dung, cung nhu cac cua hang, nha phan phoi dang bay ban tran lan san pham mu bao hiem kem chat luong cac loai...', '', 'Cho tin hieu tu Bo Cong Thuong\r\nLao Dong so 283 Ngay 12/12/2009&nbsp;Cap nhat: Thu Bay, 12/12/2009 - 7:33 AM\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nChat luong MBH luon duoc nguoi dan quan tam.\r\n(LD) - O nuoc ta hien con mot so luong rat lon cac san pham MBH kem chat luong da va dang duoc nguoi tieu dung (NTD) mua va su dung, cung nhu cac cua hang, nha phan phoi dang bay ban tran lan san pham mu bao hiem kem chat luong cac loai... \r\nBao dong ve MBH kem chat luongTheo phan anh cua cac doanh nghiep san xuat (SX), kinh doanh (KD) MBH phia Nam, hien tren thi truong co rat nhieu loai mu khong ro nguon goc, xuat xu, khong dat tieu chuan chat luong ma van duoc bay ban tai cac dia phuong. Cac san pham do duoc SX, nhap khau, bat chap su an toan cua NTD va loi dung cac ''lo hong'' trong quan ly de tieu thu voi gia rat ''beo''.&nbsp; Theo Chi cuc Tieu chuan Do luong Chat luong (TCDLCL) tinh Binh Duong, vua qua chi cuc phoi hop voi QLTT cac huyen, thi to chuc 5 dot kiem tra chat luong MBH o cac cua hang. Tich thu, tieu huy 222 chiec MBH khong dat tieu chuan. Da xuat hien them nhieu cua hang ban MBH tre em voi nhieu loai mu kem chat luong, hang gia, hang nhai cac san pham uy tin nhu: Hongda nhai Honda, Amaro nhai Amoro... Gia nhung chiec mu nay kha re, mu tre em tu 10.000 - 15.000 dong/chiec, mu nguoi lon dao dong tu 30.000 - 35.000 dong/chiec trong khi gia san pham chinh hang tu 130.000 - 180.000 dong/chiec. Chi cuc QLTT TP. Ho Chi Minh cung cho biet, tren cac tuyen duong nhu Dien Bien Phu, Xo Viet Nghe Tinh (Binh Thanh), An Duong Vuong (quan 5), Nguyen Van Linh (quan 7), Tran Nao, Luong Dinh Cua (quan 2), Phan Van Tri (quan Go Vap)... co kha nhieu sap kinh doanh MBH di dong voi gia ban chi 30.000 - 35.000 dong/cai, mau ma rat bat mat, nhieu kieu dang. Tai Ha Noi, tren cac tuyen duong nhu pho Hue, Dinh Cong, duong Lang... mu bao hiem kem chat luong duoc bay ban voi gia chi tu 20.000-30.000d/chiec voi du cac chung loai, mau ma.Cho tin hieu tu Bo Cong Thuong Trong mot van ban gui Bo Khoa hoc va Cong nghe (KHCN), Bo Cong Thuong (CT), Tong cuc Tieu chuan Do luong Chat luong, cac DN SX-KD MBH phia nam kien nghi, cac co quan quan ly nha nuoc can co nhung bien phap that cu the de giai quyet tan goc nan MBH khong dat chat luong dang luu thong tren thi truong. Nha nuoc can dua mat hang nay vao danh muc hang hoa dac biet duoc SX va KD co dieu kien. Ngay tu nam 2008, Bo KHCN cung da kien nghi Thu tuong Chinh phu cho phep bo sung MBH vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien duoc quy dinh tai Nghi dinh so 59/2006/ND- CP ngay 12.6.2006 cua Chinh phu quy dinh chi tiet Luat Thuong mai ve hang hoa, dich vu cam KD, han che KD va KD co dieu kien. Tuy vay, Bo Cong thuong lai duoc Chinh phu giao nhiem vu ra soat, cap nhat danh muc hang hoa dich vu theo nghi dinh noi tren, vi vay viec MBH co dua vao danh muc do hay khong, quy dinh ra sao, thuc hien nhu the nao... van phai cho tin hieu tu Bo Cong Thuong.\r\nHong Anh', '', '', 1, 1260844464, 'dcsor57hn2ob48388s60dpno25'),
(67, 68, 2, 'NEN DUA MU BAO HIEM VAO DANH MUC HANG HOA KINH DOANH CO DIEU KIEN', '', 'Nen dua mu bao hiem vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien\r\n\r\n\r\nThu ba, 15/12/2009 07:56\r\nhttp://www.congan.com.vn/vie/news/news_printpreview.php?catid=1101&amp;id=42336\r\n(CATP) Hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu&nbsp;kien la nhung nganh nghe ma luat, phap lenh, nghi dinh quy dinh cac dieu kien hay yeu cau ma doanh nghiep phai dap ung khi kinh doanh cac nganh nghe do. Theo do, dieu kien kinh doanh duoc the hien duoi hai hinh thuc: giay phep kinh doanh do co quan nha nuoc co tham quyen cap va cac dieu kien quy dinh ve tieu chuan chuyen mon ky thuat, cong nghe, ve sinh moi truong, VSATTP, an toan giao thong... Nhieu hang hoa, dich vu lien quan den suc khoe con nguoi thuong nam trong danh muc nay nhu: dich vu y te, thuc pham thuoc danh muc thuc pham co nguy co cao, nghe xong hoi, khu trung... Tuy nhien mu bao hiem (MBH) lai chua â€œco matâ€ trong danh muc nay du day la san pham hang ngay van cung chung ta ra duong de giup giam thuong ton vung dau neu khong may xay ra tai nan giao thong.', '', 'Nen dua mu bao hiem vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien\r\n\r\n\r\nThu ba, 15/12/2009 07:56- theo bao Cong An Tp.HCM\r\nhttp://www.congan.com.vn/vie/news/news_printpreview.php?catid=1101&amp;id=42336\r\n(CATP) Hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu&nbsp;kien la nhung nganh nghe ma luat, phap lenh, nghi dinh quy dinh cac dieu kien hay yeu cau ma doanh nghiep phai dap ung khi kinh doanh cac nganh nghe do. Theo do, dieu kien kinh doanh duoc the hien duoi hai hinh thuc: giay phep kinh doanh do co quan nha nuoc co tham quyen cap va cac dieu kien quy dinh ve tieu chuan chuyen mon ky thuat, cong nghe, ve sinh moi truong, VSATTP, an toan giao thong... Nhieu hang hoa, dich vu lien quan den suc khoe con nguoi thuong nam trong danh muc nay nhu: dich vu y te, thuc pham thuoc danh muc thuc pham co nguy co cao, nghe xong hoi, khu trung... Tuy nhien mu bao hiem (MBH) lai chua â€œco matâ€ trong danh muc nay du day la san pham hang ngay van cung chung ta ra duong de giup giam thuong ton vung dau neu khong may xay ra tai nan giao thong. \r\n\r\nMBH dom ban tran lan tren via he\r\nCac quy dinh nghiem ngat cua Tong cuc Do luong chat luong nhu MBH phai dat chuan QCVN 2:2008/ BKHCN de nham giam thieu hang kem chat luong nhung tren thuc te, nhieu co so san xuat van tung hang dom, dan tem dom de ban. Tai nhieu hoi thao ve ATGT, cac nha khoa hoc dua ra y kien rang, chung ta da lam rat tot viec tuyen truyen de nguoi dan dong tinh doi MBH nhung chat luong MBH lai la van de can ban vi van con rat nhieu vu TNGT ma nguoi bi nan tu vong do doi MBH kem chat luong. De nguoi dan hoan toan tin tuong vao mot chu truong dung nham dam bao suc khoe cho nguoi tieu dung thi viec dua MBH vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien la can thiet. Dau thang 10-2009, cac doanh nghiep san xuat MBH co chat luong o phia Nam da co kien nghi gui Bo KHCN de xuat yeu cau muon dua MBH vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien. Ngay sau do, Bo KHCN da co cong van so 3286/BKHCN phuc dap cho biet tu cuoi thang 12-2008, Bo KHCN da co cong van bao cao va kien nghi Thu tuong Chinh phu cho phep bo sung MBH vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien duoc quy dinh tai Nghi dinh so 59/2006/ND-CP. Ngay 21-9-2009, Bo KHCN tiep tuc co cong van so 2383/BKHCN de nghi bo sung MBH vao danh muc san xuat co dieu kien de viec san xuat, kinh doanh di vao ne nep. Vi nam trong linh vuc kinh doanh nen van de dua MBH vao danh muc hang hoa kinh doanh co dieu kien da duoc Chinh phu giao nhiem vu cho Bo Cong thuong ra soat de dua vao danh muc. Viec dua MBH vao danh muc san xuat co dieu kien xuat phat tu thuc te nguoi dan can duoc cung cap san pham co chat luong dong thoi gop phan dua viec san xuat va tieu thu MBH vao quy cu, ne nep. Thiet nghi Bo Cong thuong nen som len ke hoach, giai quyet van de nay de ung ho cac nha san xuat chan chinh cung nhu lam yen long dan.\r\nP.V&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1265084766, 'dkjge068o62v21d3n17jnf05g2'),
