(70, 70, 2, 'CTY CHI THANH V.N niem yet gia ban san pham MU BAO HIEM thong nhat tren toan quoc', '', 'NIEM YET GIA BAN MU BAO HIEM CHITA, OMONO, SAFE\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De giai quyet, khac phuc tinh trang san pham bi nhai gia, gia ban san pham khong thong nhat gia giua cac vung mien lam nguoi tieu dung hoang mang, dong thoi de khang dinh chat luong san pham va uy tin thuong hieu, tu ngay 1/1/2010 CTY CHI THANH V.N quyet dinh niem yet gia ban MU BAO HIEM CHITA, OMONO, SAFE thong nhat tren toan quoc.&nbsp;', '', 'NIEM YET GIA BAN MU BAO HIEM CHITA, OMONO, SAFE\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; De giai quyet, khac phuc tinh trang san pham bi nhai gia, gia ban san pham khong thong nhat gia giua cac vung mien lam nguoi tieu dung hoang mang, dong thoi de khang dinh chat luong san pham va uy tin thuong hieu, tu ngay 1/1/2010 CTY CHI THANH V.N quyet dinh niem yet gia ban MU BAO HIEM CHITA, OMONO, SAFE thong nhat tren toan quoc. \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Theo do moi san pham chinh hang cua cong ty se duoc gan kem 1 toi buom nho the hien gia niem yet va thong tin san pham de nguoi tieu dung nhan dien.&nbsp;', '', '', 1, 1262587692, 'tlcnnhnrqvse608l2vnpfivhl6'),
(71, 73, 2, 'Bi an cong nghe lam mu bao hiem...gia', '', 'Theo http://tintuc.xalo.vn/00580003606/bi_an_cong_nghe_lam_mu_bao_hiem_gia.html\r\n\r\nBi an cong nghe lam mu bao hiem...gia\r\n\r\n\r\n(24h) - Khong can giay phep kinh doanh, khong can nha may san xuat, khong can dang ky san pham dat chat luong, van co the san xuat ra duoc mot chiec non bao hiem (NBH) thu thiet, gia thap, up dat ngao nghe tren dau? \r\nTrong vai nguoi di mua tem (CR, CS), chung toi dao quanh truc duong Ly Thai To, phuong 2 quan 3 TPHCM â€“ duoc menh danh la trung tam in an tem gia de tim mua tem chat luong. The nhung, go cua gan chuc cua hang, van chua duoc mot noi nao nhan in tem. Bi the, chung toi den hoi tham bac tai xe om dang dau xe goc duong Nguyen Dinh Chieu - Ly Thai To. Bac tai xe om bao, toi chi cho co cau nhung phai co boi duong do! Toi dui voi vao tay bac tai to 100.000 dong roi chay xe theo. Vua dung xe tai dich vu ten P.D nam tren duong Ly Thai To phuong 2 quan 3, ba chu tiem hoi ngay: â€œAnh can bao nhieu, tu 1.000 cai tro len chung toi moi nhan lam, gia 400 dong/caiâ€. Thay chung toi ngo ngac, ba chu tiep loi: â€œAnh tai xe xe om dan anh den la toi du biet roiâ€. Noi doan ba chu ghi nhanh cho toi bien nhan, hen 3 hom sau den lay. Vua ghi, ba chu vua noi: â€œChung toi chi lam tem khung hinh chu nhat thoi, khong lam khung hinh thoi, hinh tron, vi cac loai hinh ay rat kho keo khung.â€', '', 'Theo http://tintuc.xalo.vn/00580003606/bi_an_cong_nghe_lam_mu_bao_hiem_gia.html\r\n\r\nBi an cong nghe lam mu bao hiem...gia\r\n\r\n\r\n(24h) - Khong can giay phep kinh doanh, khong can nha may san xuat, khong can dang ky san pham dat chat luong, van co the san xuat ra duoc mot chiec non bao hiem (NBH) thu thiet, gia thap, up dat ngao nghe tren dau? \r\nTrong vai nguoi di mua tem (CR, CS), chung toi dao quanh truc duong Ly Thai To, phuong 2 quan 3 TPHCM â€“ duoc menh danh la trung tam in an tem gia de tim mua tem chat luong. The nhung, go cua gan chuc cua hang, van chua duoc mot noi nao nhan in tem. Bi the, chung toi den hoi tham bac tai xe om dang dau xe goc duong Nguyen Dinh Chieu - Ly Thai To. Bac tai xe om bao, toi chi cho co cau nhung phai co boi duong do! Toi dui voi vao tay bac tai to 100.000 dong roi chay xe theo. Vua dung xe tai dich vu ten P.D nam tren duong Ly Thai To phuong 2 quan 3, ba chu tiem hoi ngay: â€œAnh can bao nhieu, tu 1.000 cai tro len chung toi moi nhan lam, gia 400 dong/caiâ€. Thay chung toi ngo ngac, ba chu tiep loi: â€œAnh tai xe xe om dan anh den la toi du biet roiâ€. Noi doan ba chu ghi nhanh cho toi bien nhan, hen 3 hom sau den lay. Vua ghi, ba chu vua noi: â€œChung toi chi lam tem khung hinh chu nhat thoi, khong lam khung hinh thoi, hinh tron, vi cac loai hinh ay rat kho keo khung.â€ \r\n&nbsp;Mua tem CS. \r\n \r\nTem gia duoc bay ban.&nbsp; \r\n \r\nMut xop kem chat luong (phai).&nbsp; \r\nQua cuoc tro chuyen voi ba chu, chung toi duoc biet â€œcong ngheâ€ lam tem gia khong phuc tap lam. Ban dau la viec chup lai mau tem that, sau do hinh thanh khung va keo thanh pham. Neu tem that co 7 mau, thi tem gia duoc lam chi 2-3 mau nhung neu nhin bang truc quan, khach hang su dung rat kho phan biet. Trong luc toi lay tien dat coc, thi co hai nguoi khach hoi dat mua tem gia va tem co so san xuat NBH. Mot trong hai nguoi khach noi: â€œBa chu ghi cho toi bat ky ten co so, dia chi va so dien thoai luon nhe. Nhung nho phai ghi dia chi â€œmaâ€ nhu lan truoc ayâ€. Theo cac chu dich vu, viec lam tem vua de dang vua co thu nhap cao ma khong gap bat cu can tro nao tu cac co quan chuc nang. \r\nKhong dung lai do, voi vai nguoi moi chap chung vao nghe san xuat NBH, chung toi duoc co gioi thieu den co so T.T chuyen san xuat mut xop tren duong Nguyen Trieu Luat phuong Tan Tao quan Binh Tan. Tai day, chung toi bat gap rat nhieu nguoi den dat lam khung xop NBH. Dieu â€œthu viâ€ la nhung nguoi nay den dat hang khong cho biet ten tuoi, dia chi, tu mua hang roi tu cho hang ve. Theo chi C., chu co so tren, mut xop non co nhieu loai nhung phan lon khach den chi dat 2 loai: loai re tien (2.000 dong/cai) de san xuat non kem chat luong ban ra thi truong va loai thu hai gia cao hon (tren 10.000 dong/cai) de san xuat NBH doi pho voi co quan kiem dinh. \r\nVua noi, ba C. vua nhiet tinh tu van cho chung toi lua chon cac loai mau xop. Ba C. noi, chi can phoi nhua (tuc kieu dang cua non) thi co so nay se gia cong hinh dang mut xop giong y nhu that, tham chi la kieu dang cua nhung hang san xuat non co thuong hieu. Khi chung toi de cap den chat luong tuc do can khi co vat nhon dam vao hoac kha nang chiu tac dong khi bi va dap thi ba C. phan tran, chung toi chi nhan lam theo yeu cau cua khach hang, co khach hang noi mua mut xop ve lot... trai dua hau. Neu ho dem ve san xuat NBH trai phep thi toi cung danh chiu (!?). Cac co cau da kheo lo xa vi nguoi ta doi mu nay co sao dau, chu yeu la doi pho voi cong an thoi. \r\nSan xuat NBH: khong can giay phep \r\nNhung don vi san xuat NBH thi chang can phai dam bao bat ky tieu chuan nao, khong can co giay phep hoat dong. Do vay, cung that de hieu khi tren thi truong hien nay, NBH khong ro nguon goc, xuat xu van ton tai va chiem thi phan kha lon. Tranh thu gio giai lao cho ba chu giao hang cho khach, toi bat chuyen anh Nguyen Ngoc Hanh (Long An) - nguoi den mua mut xop de hoc chut kinh nghiem trong nghe. Anh Hanh chia se â€œduong di nuoc buocâ€ voi chung toi, san xuat loai non nay de lam, chang can phai dang ky cai gi ca. Chi can dau tien dat mua 500 cai mut xop NBH. Sau do dat tiep 500 vo nhua NBH o noi khac; cuoi cung dat 500 cai quai cung voi cac loai kieng, oc vit, ... dem tat ca cac chi tiet tren ve nha lap rap. \r\nTuy nhien, cung co mot chut rac roi la do linh kien la hang troi noi, thu gom tu nhieu moi nen kho tranh khoi tinh trang â€œrau ong no cam cam ba kiaâ€. Vi vay, de non dep, bat mat thi nen dung dao cao bot vo nhua hay mut xop de lap cho vua van. Viec sau cung la quet mot lop keo mong dan mut xop vao vo NBH. Loai keo gia re nay duoc ban tran lan tai xa Vinh Loc B huyen Binh Chanh, huong lo 2, huong lo 3 quan Binh Tan,... noi co rat nhieu lo san xuat keo chuyen nau tu bich ni long, nhua phe thai thu luom o bai rac. \r\nCong doan cuoi cung, de khach hang â€œyen tamâ€ su dung hang thi phai dan tem (CR, CS) va nhan co so san xuat â€œmaâ€ len NBH. Nhu vay, da co NBH ban ra thi truong voi loi nhuan gap nhieu lan so voi cac don vi san xuat NBH chan chinh ma khong gap bat cu tro ngai nao. Day chinh la loai NBH hien tai duoc tieu thu manh nhat, do mot so co so san xuat loi dung ke ho cac quy dinh ve thanh, kiem tra cua cac co quan quan ly nha nuoc ve chat luong de san xuat va tieu thu loai hang nay.', '', '', 1, 1263023054, '6604p6ifs5nv35lgcqb923nne3'),
(72, 69, 2, 'RO LEN NHIEU MU BAO HIEM KEM CHAT LUONG', '', 'Mau MBH kem chat luong gia hang xuat xu Thai Lan.\r\n(LD) - Ngay 14.1, Chi cuc Quan ly thi truong TPHCM cho biet, gan day tren thi truong TPHCM dang ro len nhieu loai mu bao hiem (MBH) kem chat luong, gia nhan hieu de lua nguoi tieu dung. \r\n\r\nTham chi, gan day tren thi truong con xuat hien loai MBH cach dieu, hoan toan khong co xop, khong dam bao an toan cho nguoi su dung.', '', 'Ro len nhieu loai mu bao hiem kem chat luong\r\nLao Dong so 12 Ngay 15/01/2010&nbsp;Cap nhat: 6:59 AM, 15/01/2010\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMau MBH kem chat luong gia hang xuat xu Thai Lan.\r\n(LD) - Ngay 14.1, Chi cuc Quan ly thi truong TPHCM cho biet, gan day tren thi truong TPHCM dang ro len nhieu loai mu bao hiem (MBH) kem chat luong, gia nhan hieu de lua nguoi tieu dung. \r\n\r\nTham chi, gan day tren thi truong con xuat hien loai MBH cach dieu, hoan toan khong co xop, khong dam bao an toan cho nguoi su dung.Ngay 13.1, doi chuyen chong hang gia 3A kiem tra 3 sap kinh doanh 5A, 6A va 7A tai cho Binh Tay, quan 6, thu giu hon 600 mu bao hiem (MBH) cac loai. Trong so nay, hon 50 MBH co dau hieu hang gia nhan hieu cua Thai Lan, gan 150 MBH tuy dan tem CR nhung chat luong kem. Ngoai ra, luc luong kiem tra con phat hien hang tram MBH dan tem CS dang duoc kinh doanh du loai MBH dan tem nay khong con duoc luu hanh tren thi truong. Chi cach day vai ngay, ngay 6.1, doi 3A kiem tra kho hang va chi nhanh Cty TNHH AA Chau tai 414/7 va 414/8 Tan Ky Tan Quy, quan Tan Phu phat hien hon 800 MBH thanh pham gia cac nhan hieu nhu Yamaha, Honda, Andes. Luc luong kiem tra con tam giu gan 5.000 MBH thanh pham chua cong bo hop quy, chua du dieu kien de luu thong. Ong Ly Ngoc Thang, Doi truong Doi QLTT 3A cho biet: ''Thoi gian gan day, tren thi truong xuat hien kha nhieu loai MBH kem chat luong, duoc bay ban cong khai. Dieu dang noi la muc do vi pham ngay cang co chieu huong tang len. Cac loai MBH kem chat luong hien nay con ghi chu Thai Lan tren san pham de danh lua nguoi tieu dung la hang ngoai nhap. Rieng doi voi loai MBH cach dieu - MBH thoi trang, gan day luc luong kiem tra con phat hien thuc chat chi co phan vo nhua, khong co phan xop. Voi cau tao nhu the nay, khong nhung khong dam bao an toan cho nguoi su dung ma nguoi su dung co the gap nguy hiem hon khi gap phai tai nan''. Khao sat thi truong cho thay, nhung doi tuong san xuat MBH kem chat luong da ngay cang muu meo hon trong viec qua mat cac co quan chuc nang. Hien nay, san pham ma cac cong ty san xuat hang kem chat luong dua ra thi truong co 3 dac diem: Dan tem nhap khau tu Thai Lan nhung nguoi phan phoi, kinh doanh san pham khong xuat trinh duoc chung tu nhap khau hay kiem tra chat luong hang hoa; tren nhan mac khong the hien ten san pham, cong bo chat luong; cau tao cua mot so mau mu ''hot'' hien nay chi co lot vo nhua va vai lot, rat nhe va rat thoi trang nen duoc mot so NTD tre tuoi ua chuong nhung cau tao mu bao hiem hoan toan trai voi quy chuan QCVN 02:2008/BKHCN.\r\n\r\nM.THOA', '', '', 1, 1263606100, '1eu3bdrmtlp2tsbe98irmuc9i7');
