(73, 71, 2, 'Bat nhao thi truong non bao hiem', '', 'Bat nhao thi truong non bao hiem Cap nhat: &nbsp; 14:12:00 29/6/2009 \r\n(Theo bao Cong Thuong)\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nChua bao gio thi truong non bao hiem o Tp. Ho Chi Minh lai no ro nhu hien nay. Khong con bao lau nua, tre em ngoi tren xe gan may cung nguoi lon cung phai doi non bao hiem, gop phan lam cho thi truong ban non ban hiem chon ron han len. \r\n&nbsp; \r\nCongThuong -&nbsp;Tren duong Truong Chinh, Cach Mang Thang Tam (Q.Tan Binh), nhung diem ban le non bao hiem duoc trung bay kha bat mat. Tuy nhien hang hoa o day du moi chung loai, nhan mac nhu ma tran, xau tot lan lon, kho be phan biet. Ghe vao mot diem ban non&nbsp;bao hiem di dong tren duong Truong Chinh toi thay bang gia 35.000 dong/chiec, re den bat ngo. Chua kip tat may xe, co ban hang da don da: anh mua non&nbsp;bao hiem di, gia chi dang chung hai to pho. Anh mua cho ba xa hay con gai, con trai, bao nhieu tuoi de em lua cho, dam bao khong ung y khong an tien, non cua em dep, mau bat mat ma lai hop thoi trang(!).', '', 'Bat nhao thi truong non bao hiem Cap nhat: &nbsp; 14:12:00 29/6/2009 \r\n(Theo bao Cong Thuong)\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nChua bao gio thi truong non bao hiem o Tp. Ho Chi Minh lai no ro nhu hien nay. Khong con bao lau nua, tre em ngoi tren xe gan may cung nguoi lon cung phai doi non bao hiem, gop phan lam cho thi truong ban non ban hiem chon ron han len. \r\n&nbsp; \r\nCongThuong -&nbsp;Tren duong Truong Chinh, Cach Mang Thang Tam (Q.Tan Binh), nhung diem ban le non bao hiem duoc trung bay kha bat mat. Tuy nhien hang hoa o day du moi chung loai, nhan mac nhu ma tran, xau tot lan lon, kho be phan biet. Ghe vao mot diem ban non&nbsp;bao hiem di dong tren duong Truong Chinh toi thay bang gia 35.000 dong/chiec, re den bat ngo. Chua kip tat may xe, co ban hang da don da: anh mua non&nbsp;bao hiem di, gia chi dang chung hai to pho. Anh mua cho ba xa hay con gai, con trai, bao nhieu tuoi de em lua cho, dam bao khong ung y khong an tien, non cua em dep, mau bat mat ma lai hop thoi trang(!). \r\nO mot diem ban non&nbsp;bao hiem khac tren duong nay, gia chi co 30.000 dong/chiec. Khi duoc hoi gia ban 30.000d thi chat luong ra sao? Co ban hang tra loi kha that tha: gia 30 ngan la non em ban cho dan xe om, nguoi lao dong ngheo, ho mua doi chu yeu doi pho voi canh sat giao thong (CSGT). Anh tinh, cu moi lan bi thoi phat khong doi non gap hon 4 lan non binh dan ma em ban o day, con chat luong thi non nay dap xuong dat vo lien ha, boi the moi co gia beo nhu vay. Con anh muon non tot, co tem bao dam cua nha san xuat, em cung co luon. Tuy nhien gia hoi cao loai 80.000- 100.000- 120.000- 150.000- 200.000 ngan dong/chiec... tuy theo kieu dang, chat luong nhap khau hay duoc lam o trong nuoc. Khach mua moi non, bon em chi loi co vai ngan thoi, truoc em cung la cong nhan, may thang roi that nghiep, co nguoi gioi thieu bo moi ban kiem song qua ngay. \r\nChung toi vong qua cac quan 10, 5, 6, 11â€¦ thi phan lon cac cua hang, cua hieu co dang ky kinh doanh han hoi deu bay ban non bao hiem cua nha san xuat uy tin, co dan tem kiem dinh chat luong. Song gia thi tien nao cua ay, tu 100 den vai tram ngan mot chiec. Con loai non bao hiem o diem ban di dong ven duong Nam Ky Khoi nghia quan 3 cung de gia 35.000 dong/chiec thi chat luong khong khac gi o diem ban ven duong Truong Chinh, quan Tan Phu, Tan Binh, duong Nguyen Huu Canh, quan Binh Thanh, TP. Ho Chi Minhâ€¦. \r\nNon bao hiem chat luong kem khong chi duoc tieu thu kha nhieu tai cac quan, huyen o TP. Ho Chi Minh, cac tinh Dong Nai, Binh Duong ma con tung hoanh o khu vuc Tay Nguyen. Tuy la vung sau, vung xa, nhung nho trung mua ca phe va cac loai nong san khac nen cuoc song cua ba con dong bao o cac xa huyen Krong Bong co bat an, bat de, phan lon cac ho gia dinh deu mua sam duoc xe gan may. Tuy nhien viec cung ung non bao hiem cho dong bao vung xa nay thi chu yeu dua vao mang luoi ban buon, ban le cua tu nhan nen chat luong hau nhu chang co ai kiem soat, nhieu nguoi ham re mua do dom nham doi pho voi CSGT la chinh. \r\nDi xe gan may phan khoi lon ma su dung non bao hiem kem chat luong qua la dieu khong on, nhat la doi voi dong bao vung sau vung xa, duong sa o huyen Krong Bong chua tot. Anh Tran Mau Quyet, Chu tich UBND xa Giang Mao tran tro: kinh phi thi xa khong co, vi vay chinh quyen da lien he duoc nha tai tro dem non BH tot ve tan xa thu doi cho dong bao. Moi nguoi duoc doi mot non dom lay non that bu them vai chuc ngan dong nen duoc nhieu nguoi dan huong ung. Dot dau, chi hon 2 gio dong ho tai van phong UBND xa da thu doi het veo vai thung dung non BH, nguoi den sau duoc nha tai tro hen nhung ngay ke tiep se chuan bi luong non BH nhieu hon de tai thu doi. \r\nChung toi den khu dan cu o huyen Chu Prong, tinh Gia Lai, nhin be ngoai co ve dong bao noi day chap hanh luat giao thong rat tot. Tuy nhien phan lon non&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;ma nguoi dan noi day su dung chua dam bao chat luong, boi theo loi nguoi dan ma chung toi gap, cu co nguoi ban la ho mua ve su dung. Ong Tran Huu Huy, mot nha nong trong ca phe o huyen Chu Prong cho biet: thoi thi ra duong co chiec non&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;la duoc roi, de doi pho voi CSGT hon la dem lai su an toan cho chinh ban than minh. \r\nThoi diem tre em tren 3 tuoi ngoi xe may cung cha me phai doi non&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;khong con xa nua. Cac nha san xuat, nhap khau non&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;chat luong tot lieu co the dap ung nhu cau thi truong hay khong, hien dang la mot cau hoi ma du luan quan tam. Thi truong non bao hiem dang co su canh tranh khoc liet giua non&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;dat chat luong va hang gia, hang nhai kem chat luong. Lam gi de khong con mu&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;kem chat luong, giup nguoi tieu dung an toan khi luu thong tren duong pho? De giai bai toan nay thiet nghi can co su phoi hop ca 3 ben: nha san xuat, nguoi tieu dung va cac co quan chuc nang. Do la cac nha san xuat chan chinh can nghien cuu dua ra thi truong nhung san pham mu&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;chat luong cao voi muc gia hop ly cho moi doi tuong tieu dung. Thu 2 chinh ban than nguoi tieu dung phai y thuc duoc viec doi mu&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;la bao ve sinh mang cua chinh minh khi tham gia luu thong. Vi vay can lua chon cac san pham tot chu khong nen tham re, mua hang rom de doi pho voi CSGT. Thu 3 cac co quan chuc nang can kiem soat chat che thi truong va co nhung xu phat nghiem minh ca nguoi ban lan nguoi san xuat mu&nbsp;bao hiem&nbsp;kem chat luong hay hang gia, hang nhai.\r\nQuoc Khanh', '', '', 1, 1265076801, 'ddperqa853pvhg0jdbs7dltf94'),
