(26, 100, 2, 'Canh Quat Tao Oxy', 'OxyGen-Producing propeller', '', '', '\r\n\r\nCanh Quat&nbsp;Tao&nbsp;Oxy&nbsp;la san pham phuc vu cho nganh nuoi trong thuy hai san, co tac dung tao bot nuoc lam gia tang ham luong oxy trong nuoc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n1.&nbsp;Nguyen lieu san xuat: Nhua Copolymer Polypropylen (nhua PP) chiu va dap cao va phu gia chong tia cuc tim (UV).\r\n2. Dac tinh san pham : \r\n\r\nCanh quat co nhieu dang lo khac nhau voi ket cau vung chac tao nhieu bot nuoc, lam tang ham luong oxy, tao moi truong song thuan loi giup cac loai thuy san phat trien tot.\r\n\r\n\r\nBac cua truc quat lam bang dong thau hoac thep khong ri dam bao cho quat luon van hanh on dinh. \r\nBac cua truc quat co duong kinh lo: 34,5 mm. \r\nCo kha nang chiu duoc su va dap manh va nhiet do cao cua anh nang mat troi. \r\nGon, nhe de van chuyen va su dung. \r\nThich hop dung ca trong moi truong nuoc man lan nuoc ngot. \r\nTrong luong, kich co va mau sac da dang theo yeu cau cua khach hang.&nbsp; \r\nChat luong san pham on dinh.\r\nChe do bao hanh: San pham duoc bao hanh 1 nam, trong qua trinh su dung neu co van de hay thac mac gi ve mat ky thuat, qui khach co the lien he voi dai ly gan nhat de duoc ho tro ky thuat va bao hanh san pham.&nbsp;\r\nDe biet them thong tin chi tiet ve san pham, vui long lien he:\r\nVPGD: 122 Vanh Dai Trong, P.Binh Tri Dong B, quan Binh Tan, Tp.Ho Chi MinhDien thoai : 08. 3817 0401 - Fax: 08. 3817 0408Nhan vien phu trach kinh doanh: Co THUYMobile: 01699 209 891', '<P align=center><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt='''' align=baseline src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/hinh1_en_1165428454.jpg''></P>\r\n<P></P>\r\n<P><STRONG>OXYGEN-PRODUCING PROPELLER</STRONG> is a product serving aquaculture by producing foam to increase oxygen in water.</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=''WIDTH: 229px; HEIGHT: 231px'' border=0 hspace=0 alt='''' align=left src=''http://www.chithanhvn.com/upload/hinh2_1163389785.jpg''></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>1.&