(225, 100, 33, 'Mu bao hiem', '', '', '', '\r\n    \r\n        \r\n            \r\n            \r\n                \r\n                    \r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                            \r\n                                \r\n                                    \r\n                                    MU BAO HIEM \r\n                                    CHITA, OMONO, SAFE\r\n                                    ***\r\n                                    \r\n                                    &nbsp; TH&Ocirc;NG TIN&nbsp; CAU TAO v&agrave; DAC T&Iacute;NH SAN PHAM\r\n                                    \r\n                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            \r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                                                    Th&acirc;n mu duoc san xuat tu nhua ABS ch&iacute;nh pham c&ugrave;ng mot so phu gia dac biet n&ecirc;n c&oacute; be mat nhan min, chiu duoc su va dap manh v&agrave; d&acirc;m xuy&ecirc;n cao, dam bao an to&agrave;n toi da cho nguoi su dung. \r\n                                                    Lop dem xop b&ecirc;n trong d&agrave;y, c&oacute; be mat danh chac, hap thu xung dong tot. \r\n                                                    D&acirc;y quai n&oacute;n c&oacute; do chiu luc cao. \r\n                                                    Bo kho&aacute; n&oacute;n an to&agrave;n, de g&agrave;i, de mo nhung kh&ocirc;ng bi tuot. \r\n                                                    Cau tao gon nhe voi nhung lo th&ocirc;ng gi&oacute; duoc bo tr&iacute; th&iacute;ch hop tao cam gi&aacute;c thoai m&aacute;i, th&ocirc;ng tho&aacute;ng, ph&ugrave; hop voi kh&iacute; hau nhiet doi v&agrave; mat do giao th&ocirc;ng d&agrave;y dac cua Viet Nam. \r\n                                                    M&agrave;u sac v&agrave; kieu d&aacute;ng da dang, thiet ke ph&ugrave; hop thoi trang v&agrave; thi hieu cua nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng. \r\n                                                    Trong luong v&agrave; k&iacute;ch co n&oacute;n ph&ugrave; hop voi the trang cua nguoi Viet Nam, tao cho nguoi doi cam gi&aacute;c vua van, chac chan v&agrave; an to&agrave;n.\r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                                                - Mu&nbsp;bao hiem cua C&Ocirc;NG TY NHUA CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N c&oacute; 3 nh&atilde;n hieu ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; : CHITA - OMONO -&nbsp;SAFE voi k&iacute;ch co , kieu d&aacute;ng v&agrave; m&agrave;u sac da dang.\r\n                                                (Click v&agrave;o logo de tham khao mau m&atilde; san pham)&nbsp;\r\n                                                \r\n                                            \r\n                                        \r\n                                    \r\n                                    \r\n                                    \r\n                                    &nbsp;\r\n                                    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n                                    - Voi chat luong san pham v&agrave; uy t&iacute;n thuong hieu d&atilde; khang dinh, CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N d&atilde; v&agrave; dang kh&ocirc;ng ngung ph&aacute;t trien mo rong he thong dai l&yacute; ph&acirc;n phoi tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quoc. Theo d&oacute;, c&ocirc;ng ty lu&ocirc;n&nbsp;x&acirc;y dung,&nbsp;doi moi&nbsp;nhung ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng ph&ugrave; hop cho c&aacute;c cap dai l&yacute; v&agrave; nh&agrave; ph&acirc;n phoi.( Vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n he ve VPGD de t&igrave;m hieu th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch dai l&yacute; neu c&oacute; nhu cau)\r\n                                    &nbsp;\r\n                                    - De giai quyet, khac phuc t&igrave;nh trang san pham bi nh&aacute;i gia, gi&aacute; b&aacute;n san pham kh&ocirc;ng thong nhat gi&aacute; giua c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng mien l&agrave;m nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng hoang mang, dong thoi de khang dinh chat luong san pham v&agrave; uy t&iacute;n thuong hieu, ng&agrave;y 1/1/2010 CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N d&atilde; thuc hien ni&ecirc;m yet gi&aacute; b&aacute;n MU BAO HIEM CHITA, OMONO, SAFE thong nhat tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quoc. (Gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m yet duoc the hien tr&ecirc;n tem th&ocirc;ng tin san pham d&iacute;nh k&egrave;m&nbsp;theo moi&nbsp;san pham de nguoi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng tham khao. )\r\n                                    - Voi d&acirc;y chuyen, c&ocirc;ng nghe san xuat kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n; he thong quan l&yacute;, kiem so&aacute;t chat luong chat che, v&agrave; doi ngu thiet ke chuy&ecirc;n nghiep, CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N l&agrave; doi t&aacute;c d&aacute;ng tin cay cua c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; nhu cau gia c&ocirc;ng, thiet ke mu bao hiem theo y&ecirc;u cau. C&aacute;c doi t&aacute;c d&atilde; v&agrave; dang tin d&ugrave;ng san pham cua CTY CH&Iacute; TH&Agrave;NH V.N : Tap Do&agrave;n Mai Linh, Cty Duoc Pham Imexpharm, Cty Kem Nghia, Ng&acirc;n H&agrave;ng S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, Thuc an nhanh KFC, C&ocirc;ng An Dong Nai, Canh S&aacute;t Qu&acirc;n Su&hellip;vv \r\n                                    - Mu bao hiem CHITA, OMONO, SAFE d&atilde; duoc ph&acirc;n phoi rong r&atilde;i trong he thong Si&ecirc;u Thi Co-opmart tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quoc&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (Danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c Si&ecirc;u Thi c&oacute; ph